od siding which was promptly repaired.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pam Drexler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ306KcKZTKZIYxihN4LaSXvq4UBMoPxJMt-d_4leFUDgu21Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The entire process was 5 star!  I got 6 bids, and they were all great and mostly competitive.  Colt with Rock Roofing was sincere, professional, extremely responsive throughout the project and beyond conclusion. Honestly, he was not high pressure, but set his company apart from the others. He was so very helpful with the plethora of questions I sent to him.\nThe work crew was efficient and went above and beyond with the weather they experienced.  There was not a wasted minute, as they worked hard, fast and efficiently.  Love the new roof and SO GLAD I had this great experience with Colt, the install team and Rock Roofing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2ztcdkT2j_nMm4tQkCdDKL1il-G0gbAXTepjkwOUF5wmJqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hired Rock Roofing to replace my roof and gutters. I have always gotten 3 bids for any work I have done on my home but this time I only got 1. I had glowing recommendations from my daughter and several of her neighbors so I hired them without getting any other bids. They did an exceptional job from the beginning. Answering questions, choosing materials and scheduling all went very smoothly. The roof and gutters look great and I am very happy with their efficiency and cleanup. I would not hesitate to hire them again. I worked with Colt who is the Project Coordinator. He is a real asset to the company!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeremy Limones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVU8JSOYrXIXH9S2hUq1vvuFVoQY2CWNkMIDIyTNW9kVmnlgU7d=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rock Roofing deserves a solid five stars for their work and now that it’s been a full year, I can confidently say the roof is holding up beautifully. Recently, I had a small issue that needed a professional look, so I gave them a call. Their customer service was absolutely top-notch, quick response, clear communication, and genuine care from start to finish.\n\nIt’s rare to find a company that stands so firmly behind their work, and even rarer to find one that treats you like a priority long after the job is done. I don’t expect to need any major help anytime soon, but if I ever do, Rock Roofing will always be my go-to roofing company from here on out. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Conor Law","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2eUVfYI_VEZlumyMsMjkDN6FuoKGoM45Swg8uuh_WSs34NcA-YA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a fantastic experience working with Rock Roofing. Colt, the main project coordinator, was extremely responsive and always available to answer questions. He even went above and beyond by connecting us with other trusted vendors for related work, which was a huge help.\n\nTheir bid came in significantly more competitive than three other estimates we received, but the quality of their work and the thoroughness of their process exceeded expectations. What stood out the most was the clear and timely communication throughout the project. Whether it was updates on the schedule, coordinating around our kids’ nap times, or even arranging extra cleanup when needed, Colt and his team were thoughtful and accommodating every step of the way.\n\nReplacing a roof is a major expense, but Rock Roofing made the process smooth, professional, and surprisingly stress-free. I’d highly recommend them to anyone looking for a reliable roofing company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bojana Gugulevska","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbbCDWQl7UmRIcDvJKVC0TcAw5EUyqzgC3kw65ftd0X5MtVp1y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired rock roofing to replace the old roof on our house. They were very professional in explaining the work that will be done, how long it will take and stayed within the quoted amount.  Overall we had a great experience and I would highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lauren Setzer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVi1kH8h3ThNvgE63wfZtHcMx5HMzW4U2VIPyDloZmDuXQqu0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptional job! The team was super skillful, efficient, clean, and conscientious in their work. We appreciate all the help Scott and his team provided us in weather proofing our home for the upcoming rainy season. Despite needing a full new roof, his quoted price was very reasonable and the outcome and quality are absolutely superior! Our home is transformed from the outside, and the skylights and solar tube we added brought light and dimension to the inside of our home. 👏🏼👏🏼👏🏼 Definitely don't hesitate to book with Rock Roofing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arindam Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtn5YZrPLosiqgYuF3yx3ekJcUWc2hRzXRxW7D_L3e8AQIQc8n=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rock Roofing did the Roof replacement for our home and it was a very well done job. Easy to communicate with and sticking to their communicated schedule. The guys were through professionals and the did an awesome job replacing our worn out roof with a new one.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
