s of getting quotes to see about replacing the shingles next year, Cam's inspection turned up some serious problems that really needed to be addressed sooner rather than later. I am glad we had a fully new roof and gutters before the latest rains came in.\n\nWhile replacing a roof is never fun, the entire team at Squatch was amazing. Great communication throughout the process, a super team of 6 guys who replaced our entire roof from deck boards out, to assisting in the short term financing of the project.\nAnd it all started from a random story post I saw on Instagram. Was worth reaching out to them.\n\nI agree with what other reviews have said. The communication was great and they made sure we understood the process. The workmanship was top notch.\n\nAnd they even came all the way down to Puyallup!!!\n\nIncluding some before and after shots.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2uYNlxi7laDV81j220fMEzrK7w5dx0uou3vh7YK4Lzzm5mHCaV_br9RBP4dbGkKiVbEKgPvFtdWQFleVRjdc9BfRmcmaMx15-uxTXn_cohRov3IBeVxj_nDK5ztJWiEbAr6MkOvCynIckL=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0YalxUMQWth9kXfLscvNg88jwD84zbe0Wc-XM1pI_rAgjYM5rnYz65pPkGNbwhgbpg1fjjSPaSRbSZLxZFaQEx5WEDWewdnTHx6hteo9khY-HBlvlikJRyXKzFwQprdJlJ9-tS1u_pz6-C=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ma81j1POJR2YYexvmeiZ71QnFuUH9xCIuTdLotOmOWEq3tni9g9OOxBYG5BNvbhB1fa8_JbXUv45EU_MnP2-7K6R1592gMRTfAT_UTslMo_GJiszQ9tGn4iW4srYWLMW2kp0fJa6BYHiz=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15AXo53kjYpkWT-l9fpy7DcPzUTMow-EcboA27evl_vaJ2cYx6Slojea8u4y0unwp6qyi3GvNG21mnk5PDMj7zaUxVPeeq5ooLR9FI3EQIH2k7OmSYF4GxWDfsVw2QJPcyR_LSLLquA49z=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0klWaZJ6WYaS5OB-xndG2S8Z1O0Tgo0Z0VfA1JE1QWTYCbLEMSsWHelvzqzi1ZIwDUTL1O-mSQ0Bu03WiYjMN6GqsQJoe806Bf8Gwvg0J2I7rFBF-blvpdLKywwr62CJQPaUhvpsw55eQt=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-17"},{"Name":"Taliesin Stratton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVT9wceGxDeaNCLDki-zC1q-B_pVvxJiwukJyZ5IHtVjKyg6Sk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the very beginning, the Squatch team ensured we were set up for success. From the initial assessment with Jim, to confirming materials and timing with Danny, to Beau overseeing his crew. I also can't forget to mention the most pivotal piece - Carlos and his squad!\n\nRoofing is a major expense and undertaking that can cause anxiety and concern, especially if you've chosen the wrong company. I can say hands down we made the right decision in choosing Squatch Roofing. We were thoroughly impressed by their constant communication and professionalism, especially given the scope of our job. Carlos and his team were absolutely phenomenal! They worked tirelessly for two days, even staying late to ensure everything was taken care of. And the results prove it.\n\nOur roof looks amazing, thank you to everyone at Squatch Roofing. You truly did an incredible job. Highly recommend to anyone.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2MsB1pTQqZzXSJWhDz3P1eOHXT88-_CH_syhk3faUAiTtXK4LwSQYnD8L94QZYodwy2cQBTuNlufe5SoilRXWVT5TJEJLgs3zWEgMK78GYIozXe7QVAK1v0Q2jRebCxYnk_U4IVA_S0Yo=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-7"},{"Name":"Sungwook Moon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX53vXHlrU_LveEtYjB1vFUnJAyfhB1BUCwfFrB5bO5LfniZwDM0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From inspection, estimates to repair, I am very satisfied. The inspector took photos and videos of not only the outside but pretty much everywhere inside the attic and explained the issues in detail. The quote was reasonable and I scheduled for the repair (and they had great availability). Brian and Luke came for roof repair. They were professional and thorough in their work. They even cleaned up some gutters and went above and beyond to ensure everything is in good shape. I really appreciated their work ethics and professionalism. Communication with everyone has been smooth and courteous as well. I am thankful to my coworker who recommended Squatch roofing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna Welton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIU4dk5Ft5SZXaJqh8D_2VW03DBcnfv3K2h4sD9kwRwlNb5gA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Squatch Roofing did an excellent job in replacing my 28 year old roof. They were very professional in every way and explained the replacement process in detail. They did exactly what they said and cleaned up every day and in the end, I was very pleased! I Highly recommend them!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3SkTBJ4m2qy1SSVYhmlvhAnbOtmJX6yLdit1ynuNr1ouqVqTTO12Odff3ES5ZhKKPaFlctyEEgsZ4w4rEFo3kAppdg1HZIZG1oERqRzx-vYFP6zTcvHr5XOpnleEnSqa7Vze_BkFhr3sLd=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-21"},{"Name":"Ian Ferguson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRxFZode-jX7YLwyFA4Z8Lhi_Y_fJ4AW2pRLqGx3ECqRru8MvRqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Manny was out knocking on doors in my neighborhood offering free roof inspections which was very convenient for me as I was already thinking of having one done.\n\nJim was able to come by the next day and did a very thorough inspection of the roof, both the exterior and in my attic.  Jim did a great job explaining the results of the inspection and laying out the different options I had available to me.  The inspection also revealed a major issue not related to the roof so I'm thankful I had it done.\n\nAmazingly they had an opening in two days where they could do the work.  That's probably not typical, but I get the impression that they try to get people scheduled as soon as possible.\n\nBrian and Luke worked on my roof.  They fixed a cracked ridge cap, cleaned moss off of the shingles, cleaned the gutters, and treated the roof.  They did great work.\n\nOverall I found Squatch Roofing employees to be very knowledgeable and professional, and the service to be a great value.  I'm very happy with the whole process and will definitely use them in the future.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
