es":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gabriel Duta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUuRP3wqgc_pHKZ1I_WFLcWTpo9gVEbSpSaa1bCrsFtob_4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very happy with the roof and gutter cleaning job done by Daniel and his crew! Showed up right on time, quoted a fair price upfront, worked thoroughly and no surprises. Roof looks brand new, gutters are flowing perfectly, and they cleaned up like they were never here.\nZero complaints, total pros. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anila V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLU7qFE2obP0XwnYxWKfpIDpE9cq3qtEbQ2OYsHpZRoX2k5wQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing and thorough job! Very impressive.\n\nGot moss removed from the roof with treatment for future moss prevention.\nDaniel not only made sure that the weather was right for this job but also did a very detailed work. He made us apprised of the job every step of the way. His expertise is commendable.\nThanks Daniel.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yue Guan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEAjd7TtG24ntbAYHL1HskLknjPxCeCuYTT-HKXMKrviEH5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently hired this company for gutter repair, house painting, and roof maintenance, and I couldn’t be happier with the results.\nThe team worked very efficiently and with great attention to detail, finishing everything faster than expected.\nTheir pricing was very reasonable, especially compared to other companies I contacted, some of which quoted nearly triple the cost.\nI’m extremely satisfied with their work and have already recommended them to my friends.\nHighly professional, trustworthy, and great value — truly a 5-star experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pratik Gundawade","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9S6O348dxzpsK1AutTwRTP7dL95Y4ubtRcN39WQbwQlpduj0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently, I had the house’s gutters cleaned and received a moss treatment for my house’s roof from Daniel. He was incredibly responsive from the start, answering all my questions and keeping me updated throughout the process. The service was professional and efficient, with a quick and direct response. He helped me understand the process and shared before-and-after pictures, demonstrating great transparency in his work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xiaoying Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9Jldm9lM_VMRZyP41HD5l4htg__-ct0F3fm3kaWVFr2FzkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brixton\u0026Windsor has helped me with moss removal and gutter cleaning. They also helped with a leak caused by the built-up moss. Their response was quick and price is reasonable. They had excellent communication throughout the process and the job was done quick and clean. I will definitely recommend the service and will come back myself for any future services. Thank you Braxton\u0026Windsor!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
