 and Aaron not only offered better prices but also seemed to be waaay more knowledgeable and personal than any of the other bigger companies\n\n​If you need your roof cleaned, skip the big names call Aaron at Roof Moss Gone. You'll get way better service, and more bang for your buck.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Asmar Razzaq","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaWRL3y6WgEvFK3M27TvDHpc5Mps3qOsvCkktj-54J2GnI1GoT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Aaron did an outstanding job cleaning the roof of my home. He was extremely thorough, knowledgeable, and took great care to remove all the moss and debris from both the roof and the surrounding areas. The property was spotless when he finished — he even cleaned up all the moss that had fallen to the ground. Aaron’s attention to detail and professionalism really stood out. I’m very impressed with the quality of his work and would highly recommend his roof cleaning services to anyone looking for a reliable and skilled professional.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jim Boulter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWp6dwZZuicb6z4OBgYkdo8b2n87MUgJZ-FOIv581uWbTJwecKm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Aaron clean the roof of moss and algae.  We had only minor moss issues but wanted to stay ahead of it.  Aaron came and sprayed down the roof and it killed all the moss very quickly.  However the dead moss was white and was cosmetically undesirable on the black shingles of the roof and we were not sure if it was under the shingles or not (we are not experts, obviously).  We asked Aaron to come back and take a look and he came back and was able to very lightly scrape the dead moss off and show us that it was not causing any issues with intrusion under the shingles, so it was just ugly but not a real problem.  Aaron took the time to show me and to explain why not brushing the roof on the initial visit was the right call, which was really nice.  The only small issue we had was that our windows did get dirty from the gutter cleaning.  They are dirtier than before the cleaning now (clearly splashed from the gutter spraying), but it’s not that bad and our gutters and roof are good, plus we did not pay for window washing.  Photos are before, after initial visit, and after revisit.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1imQoY377hW93PdMYZF84lHXebZbw65GSKAS2l8hmgtmwm5wG9QNFNHliZwwtRNGxg-_VIvzXWRkZWSIFGRbQwcj4xRAkL-gwzkqUY70qv7C6hkXQgVaWr3d3hoP87ePBLEfZH=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2YiGo9258bvcU8Lx1xKN2X1jMYRyOSyOgMMH73m4HCaxzwvSLwIb6TcBtRvD3NwxH25r4snuxbTJXwbwsINn-E1-EAFZs7rFQgmpQUSKJCJ3JIAClQDh_CldtYAQAPq625qROf=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2WjGJMgVLmQpzbCLa-Hc6JwMd0Vec9FhdgVeDcj2fwV1XGtRCKxZ4p34AwAsrsByCkha9dTd4ddyhjdhZNB_gNd543-p7NMZRUCm44hE9Nsr2MnA27-MGLL3sg0cNoqQeaR5w=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-12"},{"Name":"Gail Wells","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0B2nB26yyEciIjteJ7ScULKfgNelt_F3veXvc4b8yOSsWOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely loved Aaron. Great price, immediately did our roof cleaning and treatment. Spoke to us in ways we could understand. Would recommend RMG to everyone. Thank you for great service. Also going to have yearly maintenance on roof and gutters.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1KztnfBfn1uRngl7_kDomNz-rhhYvtqSKZrsgiQvX5MRXvi4j9A4kfLIsLx9xg6Ncwg3ZT5OsQDZcNHb563t8Beb3u96yRpV1k4rDOfUlthgC4P72ZFVL8V5Pevx0NyRtJRkAZZw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0dBSq61zO29-R86RjI1LnlZVEMA6idUezHev0cws6tMxh99xVIQmSojmU7UWfZ02pQaKyuGB-Zvpo-oXIAW4o1huvFd_vrvMCSu6Ooyuo3J5RyV6dK6kIzrVmvEbzTkGh3S-1M=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2dWNZp2CPblqHSGxCiEDCnMpL_cRKy2HRqOmsW86hnEmA0JAm4NyCRdKUpVu6QKtpW3Lk06qfiIAhuyBMpG7h5h_lKs02pmzHKR7bCeeY9CnewgOIxZt476TxyWUaj9So4bsHkyg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoT