team member’s work from time to time, and Eugene followed up with me for questions and shared tons of photos everyday.\n\nA specific thing to call out is about our skylight. The original skylight is not the standard size and model. Eugene and Rene figured out a solution quickly and explained to us for approval. The solution requires additional wood frame to support the skylight. Rene painted the wood frame to match our dry wall. Check my photos, it is beautiful and looks like an original design. In the end, our skylight got upgraded to these fancy ones with remote controller, and my kid got very excited about it.\n\nOnce the project was completed, Eugene took a final check of the roof and reminded me multiple times that once the trash bin is removed from our driveway, I shall sweep the driveway again in case any nail was left.\n\nI do not have the expertise to judge if the quality of their work is really good or not, only the time will tell. But for what I experienced so far, the team is professional with their on time work, rationale to pay attention to details, in time response, and clear communication. Our new roof looks beautiful and I would recommend Diamond roofing for others to get their premium service.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3VABaGvrdL4f6yY7Gx8acev05LNC5-dlkRtDCeMctfJ87CnRCt42fpiVwCwauibsV0FJpCAGPjbDuMnffAHbreNhvA4o1mcGT114ni0bmVgOTkz9Bo7F_Z-gxaxGBq2mMY5iWU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ncYVGyaXKkEmopuxkj-2HTK1k2ySzETmE6e4FzCwXn9RQMGBiGIyBEPsF3Vlr_kFtZwIx6-nc6pMg2fJvdqFhjNkHWeIyv6XbSUKKxAXCQctLMC9fbJwKLwlqKjjl_Eg25tXykw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3HdtKnpWevz6MbBbjN5oyjZqD6Ikv1m2THLmhx3tP2_08d8ChRIIATGVzMUoc9IBHPQRFnn2lnTct88g2lGYvz_fn_kcu2fQdhePqwXIdWj1owUS_1wnLt7BNGOwdvhOcnqic=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2RIb-H0vPfAP1WRKDmgwkmHL8vCLzp-vzriZVPxVfxx-t0jsb0sifoDu2Oeilycc4WrKgIeEgI8DMu_y9y931UWEQU_A99vujMYoGVQ_Eay-rwh_glx7-KpPOEMKrk2bqHHmfd