s://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102708089946256709365"},"complete_address":{"borough":"North Industrial","street":"14102 NE 189th St","city":"Woodinville","postal_code":"98072","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Donald Hatch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-XbYeZpB3RKCAlu8gaMDKLzcTnDEx-brcRruP2nEyMrMARA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't say enough positives about this company. Starting with the free estimate through the finished work, they were friendly, professional and excellent craftsmen. They showed up when promised, cleaned up after and did a great job! I had them clean and treat the roof for moss and a year later it still looks good. We have a willow tree with long thin leaves that get everywhere.  Their gutter guards are the perfect solution. No more scary ladders on the second floor roof!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3tC-6Nbz7OxIeS1_DTpZ-1PMe8bv5N3Qp2lICaxyHRdKGEW7jYYUMZB1k43kbagGXLhbr2mbB5mUpTz46ta_xhUGs05hYMuecxTknAGx41X8qJaq_it_P0faGPV1lw1CNpewQl_btzcmk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn33pr0I2m7vuopfra8Ut_vvoJfhePk3Md9lMF7BXHtf2CxcXmUHqRnW-68eIrBhJhBg33xu3o6Bj0m3pTVCqeaabThwESQ2sn2UmOVZACQNXxX-o4fx2ubk93NId2z00g0-gzbV-g6ri00u=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-25"},{"Name":"Lori Hittle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkooTZG1ktS9ywhw5pvS15VZEjMY77hUjnSiPOBmcp3StoIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"High Point Gutter was a pleasure to work with. The estimator and crew were professional, great communicators, and their knowledge really showed. When questions came up about th