 in Seattle. He was communicative, came out to do a quote, and showed up to do the work on the day we scheduled. They even came by a few weeks later to fix a gutter cover that had been popped up by a squirrel!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nelly K.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_soV-mhNMABCBvboHBHaoqW6U4jY9FdL-CmWto2-kkq45hw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Sound Gutters and Roofing to replace our gutters and worked directly with Fritz throughout the process. He was professional, easy to work with, on time, and transparent about pricing—no hidden charges. Quality work from a reliable, family-owned business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Weber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLveS9CvUnYDRogn3OGASWSV_r3LYCK77SgINS2G-dwF8TOgg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sound Gutters did a great job on my gutter repair. They were prompt, very easy to work with, and did a thorough job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Casey Madayag","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgegMs0H3lSjvbRSIiXeflZQe5fY300Qjn75eejtrGV9NJaHdjdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quick and professional service all around. When I called regarding getting a quote for gutter repair, Fritz came the next day took a look, saw it was a quick repair and did it right on the spot! He even told me I can cancel my upcoming roof cleaning because I don't need it. He was professional and a clear subject matter expert. Will look for Sound Gutters and Roofing from now on !","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
