 proactive, professional, and schedules appointments promptly. I would definitely love to continue working with them and highly recommend their services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mark Abramson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL2JGfYF1IXP7Fuvh1ZH6PjtXGHGVa1YqsFH3BeovdFxIHcCv6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cobalt replaced some of the cedar exterior siding on our home in Kirkland.  I hired them because their bid was competitive and clear.  Kevin did a thorough job of reviewing the house and submitted a clear proposal.\nThey started the job a few days later than originally expected but Kevin communicated well through that.  The guys doing the work were professional, fast, and did a good job cleaning up at the end of the day.  And the quality of the work was very good.  There were only a few small punch list items that they took care of quickly.  They actually finished the job sooner than expected.  I'd highly recommend Cobalt for siding work and would hire them again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3nqGn94j_F_Mv3ep3Sm5lD5YOmZkZlbR8OCzyx7YdICyXz3mNhuZOb3RNMp5vZzTjYBTiW2MMVYLquf2c4iBCAb_rZ7IYB-tHH78Q732w4phH7xjNRiMdjS7kMi4VIcMyxUeV_3A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn295-lRp045eQ2Sx22z5UqsKV3yiX1fnZ6c1tgrxiB9vQv9_WmYuZkFVP8q6XGdBlH5lE4rj5UM_SmIKXrqqQDORnliZl_qpnB90cNYA5OH9_4yqZRxVLLlVLLMm1mTsdlsKWs=k-no"],"When":"2020-8-25"},{"Name":"Gordon Tang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcwxrDIUKEbfvm1UAv1NPDUfiNkq2YQHVVaVt0Hj-IJsWn0liS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We signed the siding replacement contract in May 2024 and the project was supposed to start in late Sept 2024. However, the project was delayed due to problems in the material order. We then decided to postpone the project to late May 2025. While the communications during this period was not that smooth, the project was finally started in early June 2025 after several follow ups. The crew team and the project manager, JJ was excellent. Easy to communicate and responsive.  The quality of work is very good. Unfortunately, the pre-painted siding materials were not enough and they used non pre-painted siding for some parts. Though they would paint for us, we were not happy with it and insisted not for the lower front part of our house near the main door. JJ was very patient and reported our concerns to his boss Calvin. They addressed our concerns and ordered a little bit more new pre-painted siding for the front part near the main door while painted other areas covered by non pre-painted siding. The remaining project has to be delayed for 6 weeks to receive the new materials. Their professionalism is highly appreciated. Overall speaking, though with some mishaps during the process and took longer time to complete the work, we are satisfied with the project and think that it's a good value for the finished work. We highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Logan DeMelt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeWvximXTXkF4AsM59O4SZ_wyaOHSgrW6JVrzNmRqQ9Jx4-a9nnA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This crew, lead by Kevin has gone above and beyond the call of duty in every aspect. Let me assist with a breakdown of how my experience went:\n\nThe reach out was professional and scheduled for a first meeting. We discussed options for new siding and we gave a handshake to seal our working relationship. Within that week and work started in winter conditions (rain, cold, dark).\n\nDuring demo we ran into our first snag, no layer of plywood under the existed under the current older cedar. Kevin laid out options, and we agreed to add this to the work list and materials showed up within sort order. This showed the responsiveness, prowess of the craft, and ability to handle any issue at hand.\n\nThe rest of the job finished in short order and ahead of projected timelines. A few items on the site became damaged during the demo, but, Kevin replaced them himself. It is that sort of commitment that is attractive to any future clients. I would recommend this group over all others.\n\nNow, almost months later, I text him after out of the blue on Sunday with a plumbing issue. This issue could require cutting into the siding. I asked for him to give me a call when we had a moment, he meets me straight on with a call back on potentially his only free moments off this weekend.\n\nKevin and all parties he work with are as professional as they come. I knew I made the right call going into business with him and I do believe his word is good. If you handshake on it, he will stick to it. This review is part of me living up to my agreement with him. He shook on standing by his work, and he has continued to earn nothing but praise.\n\nPlease reach out to me for any questions if you feel there is something that you need answered about this group. You might be able to find a cheaper bid, but you won't find a better group.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3FLIffbxfU_3wsSroD9eBYR_kQmrUmRSmuCBkHzIOmTn-aNVgz7Ix9MGKNdi3rwCwLO9ahGoJ399ZkFdxBJOWMN-vvnj9q8wjdRQB-waMQo4xo9og1toq-RTqhWtz9EWdHw9Fx=k-no"],"When":"2020-10-4"},{"Name":"D B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcdCMQeYGFQWbFFnyyQHkPXhLPKNn245wunjTEv5LVx42cWLI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cobalt is great they got the job done quickly \u0026 did a fantastic job. Replaced the entire roof on the home and garage plus replaced gutters. Highly recommend! Kevin, Nick and Lisa all great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWGP65wIJKl-QA-LiABq902kj-i-nMjeRgWYmFAG9fHr-87bwg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had the siding on the front of our house replaced and are very happy with the job. Communication was great. My husband and I both work from home and they were so quiet and finished the job fast. Would not hesitate to hire again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0EiOdv6nxm_gHTtL84ptdNuQR5U-ZjaULJUrJaTOUMOcLbegMo4q0JX_0TELuS5QzKXd7clKywMBSH3Qe5csqOzzR9hlFNxQytfPK4sjNAcIb6ewf1q2mGZC7du8YZrq5I7EjJ3A=k-no"],"When":"2023-5-16"},{"Name":"Daniel Purcell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqnpESCMym3kFJY6VINQy-zrxit4Hf3W21FYCbCU__5msweg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kevin and the Cobalt team did unbelievable job on our new deck. When a large tree fell on our deck existing deck, Kevin and Ryan were at our house the next day to work through options and had incredibly fair quotes the day after.\n\nWe’re very pleased with the way our new TimberTech deck turned out. Much more modern than the previous build and they nailed the specs that were requested.\n\nI’d 100% recommend the Cobalt team!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
