OYk363DXSwSSvx1L-OPpKZPdIIRopE61R4VZ-RsJcI8P8vi8uRJa9WBZzV6T20iQ1S0yDcREeBktUvhC-dnXY-qmy7hGQd_0XpVI-48eUSQ=k-no"],"When":"2020-1-5"},{"Name":"sue hart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2aqSRtLDlrpeyRes1N1-A98SUXO_ziFV91b-GWbwTfaSKSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had experience with 3 different roofers and none come close to the terrific experience I have had with Ben at Allied Construction. Their work ethic is simply unmatched. I would wholeheartedly recommend them to my closest friends and family without hesitation. Ben restores my sometimes lagging faith in decent, honest, and ethical contractors. I wish he was the norm rather than the exception.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLixs1Ve_HEoomrg2qW3F3W57Y8EU2_13t1MvNCC2P88eHsbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Working with Allied Construction for my roof replacement was a great experience.  From start to finish, working with Ben and his team were great.  They were booked out a bit (summer time) but communicated the timelines to me and kept me up to date.  When the installation time came, they communicated the drop off time of the dumpster, the arrival times of the crews and the expected completion time.  When they opened it up, they found a few more things that needed to be taken care of and they made sure the job was done right.  It was HOT the days they were here, but they worked efficiently, were pleasant to have around the property (no bad language or smoking that I've experienced with other contractors) and they cleaned up meticulously.    Pricing was fair and didn't change from his estimate.  Thank you for giving me confidence the roof will be sound moving forward.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYgte01AkkDwyz8Qz0flNKaZSViEG34h_QIWDy6J66egF7Vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Allied construction does great work and stands by their work as well. Very communicative and responsive to my requests.\n\nThey updated our protective coating on our flat roof and came back after some weather to make sure the roof was adequately protected.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Herman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV49EcuBASdre3bjYc8rHuUFsN7eqHJ9Z34AFDK2FgH8dTU1S4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Allied Construction did a fantastic job working with us to replace our 20 year old roof. They were very flexible and adjusted their schedule to meet ours. The roofer was a great worker, very attentive to detail and took our concerns seriously. He did a great job roofing our house and the roof looks awesome. We would definitely recommend Allied to anybody.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa Terry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQ74cR6W-IqGwQXJ6CvjtqW6GURBkj0Crnx5fB-F0Ad-YGBx4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We decided to replace the 26-year-old composite roof on our shop with a metal roof that we can easily add solar panels to in the future. From the first email through to even after the roof was installed, Ben has been professional, responsive and patient with me and all of my questions. He and his crew did a great job and were careful to clean up the site afterward. We have been so impressed that we have scheduled Ben and his crew to replace the roof on our house this summer as well. Definitely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marcia Pettersen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIeDwaRnH6X5zTocgi7uM0liFt6kIXrBoqVw23hbIugxfR2Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ben and his crew were friendly, conscientious and punctual.  The bid from Allied was more reasonable than most we received.  They replaced our wood shingled roof with composition.  Being partial to wood, we were worried we might not like the new look, but it turned out great.\nI highly recommend Allied Construction.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
