g recognized by the US Dept. of Energy","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Lucinda Mountifield","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwMYYGMahLSXZ7vM12ek9PJWFWdmMoH-hmCbvEA2scJBxbpVfh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adrian and his crew were amazing! They insulated my whole house, wrapped my pipes, replaced my dryer and bathroom vents. I highly recommend this company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"michael bokrosh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfnL_DfXztVXiHYlB8cL9GnjO1IHbPB4f6VoiuWNjAiXt305w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They completely weatherized my house from the attic and underneath the crawl space and replaced all my old windows with new insulated units. They were very clean.They were on time. And they did great work.I highly recommend them. Michael","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Welch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3ykvXWqR1yvktJFxQSrb7IjqKzXFgw2P-Kl7tkLh08xTE6iNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adrian Vela is such a nice guy. I appreciate him and his team of skilled workers very much.\nOnce the project started, the Vela crew arrived and put in a hard days work everyday until the project was completed.\nMy home is an old farmhouse built 1906 and it needed insulation from top to bottom. Even areas that weren't originally on the work order Adrian included in the project.\nI gave Adrian a call about 2 weeks later because I noticed one small area in the basement that was missing the protective foil.\nHe responded quick and arrived a few days later. All is good.\nThanks Adrian.\nAll the best to you and your team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cathy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIACM-rw_2S1Cuy_Xj1LlYk-hAsH6fLTfCdkhUPB-zi5_2PMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adrian and his crew did a fantastic job insulating and weatherizing my home.  They showed up on time, worked steadily and did  excellent work. They cleaned up each day and treated my home and me with complete respect. I felt totally comfortable having them all in my home and would hire them again in a heartbeat.  A truly positive experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Hillman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnH6xsWyAvFgEV3vhUMHRNlEZ7Qs3qRUXtk6ZnDZ5zjSnAEDs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience with Vela Brothers INC! Adrian and his team did a fantastic job insulating my whole house and updating my fan a few months ago. They were professional, efficient, and the quality of their work exceeded my expectations. I highly recommend their services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Parchman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWO4uVe62TV5U1wWtSuAADl34YSA3elvrNeqrmUABEyuSlx3CIIBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently hired vela brothers to do the insulation in our house. It was a great decision. they were so informative when they initially came our to give us a free bid. It was so pressure free and they gave us a breakdown item by item of what work they could do for us and they left it up to us to pick what we could afford and what offered the most value for us. Once the work started I was so happy with the professionalism and genuine care they put into their work. They cleaned up everyday they were here, and the owner Adrian was actually on site and made me feel like I was so important throughout this entire process. I could not be happier with the quality work that they did, as well as the excellent customer service. I would highly recommend them to anyone that is wanting to get any work done on their home of any kind!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lori Pickering","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfsNmhTfkESrgsVJdBNFFBJoeyJ6ZvFxkiD9SfF9nQGIPZ08vS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vela Brother's did, what I think, a big weatherization project at my home. Some windows replacement, insulate 3 attic's, basement ceiling and seal hvac system etc.\nBack breaking work! Left my house clean and kept me informed through the whole process. Thank you Vela Brothers, for making my home a better place to live.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Snake Eyes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDwEVqN2WnJOa2U2d9O5bELOCbvnYNBNZde_aKCMFwWjDhejw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If I could I would give a negative. The vela brothers were hired by MDC to do some work to my house, so vela brothers was not my choice. The vela brothers not only did a poor job, they also did not finish the job, and didn't clean up there mess before they left. They left holes/cracks in my walls, nails in my ceiling, installed my hood range wrong, made white marks all over the outside of my house. They took apart the metal shelving in my kids closet and did not put it back right, so when I tried to hang up my kids clothes the shelving collapsed. Thats just some of it.The vela brothers damaged my house and destroyed my property. The vela brothers also unplugged my freezer in my garage  to use the outlet, and did not plug it back in, when I found it all my food was bad. One of the workers fell off his ladder and fell on to my AC and broke it amongst some other things. The vela brothers refused to pay for any damages, and denied they did any damage when asked by there insurance company. I tried to call the owner but kept getting hung up on. The owner of the vela brothers and his office staff called me a liar. I can't afford to fix the damaged they made so I'm stuck with it. Not only did they damage and destroy my house they insulted me. In the end I would not recommend the vela brothers.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
