nt on.  We knew some sort of replacement had to be done and went ahead and got quotes for Hardiboard siding from multiple contractors.  Green city was very competitive on a cost basis but what sold us was how much attention they paid to our concerns and needs.  Our PM John was great to work with and kept us informed throughout the process.  Once they started the work went very quickly, they even beat their original schedule estimate.  We love the new look and that our maintenance requirements have dropped dramatically.  They even swept out the garage!  Highly recommended!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn38hjrnINHL4CmvfQXiaU5TVF4Oe4GKuvlYun0sx8EPkml_-ZoBC3LtO-OxrQGkpyCuneqL4B0_1Kinzvb9nnAuUFdFRmaDdXfSIQZKnHpE2LQeWEQGydHQ6sdioST8nnbttyPi=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xXn7ieY0iHRHA4u5reZqADwCjM7yr4rVcZYcjj2MseXgqZwWBCT3DbPVjfyxnlmQhLNA4Hnc1d8qq2X-Oc7Bc80jWH0D3Ax6VYaOx8aW2MTHvyffMADinZQJYMjlGuorFNjEwKg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0dqTj9KFYHei3PhE3W8LsZ2oDPsDU-p5zK6Klf-TT-j3ESg4lE7HQKjLFUzW6sPYmGhjLuXHxV3fFhvejv5ey--ClQFqqXMDCeoJE-aUYZnIKajKLmRqUHHD3nV2yzz9CJjk9b=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Qx47xt_iLwVx1fmKLgExhn5Qh2JnhkxWHNL2EsLqmxA1Ak-Z5fvLjC3YyOgPvMygeyPH94zcs67WNttilas1klaXzFnTLL9oJJj-00e0AVjHcWQlojLkTNDB82dx8CVry-Js2cQ=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Dean Grasser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfF6F7joNxVe17ySWXeYZT5QmTpFZs1GSvZQA7tZWbcW6zIpk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My house had some windows that were original and needed to be replaced. I talked to several window companies. Some didn't want to deal with me because the project was to small. Some wanted to spend 3 hours to try to sell me a house full of windows. I made it clear I only needed 5. John from Green City come over, we looked at the windows he measured them up and gave me a price. They were ordered and replaced. His crew did a great job. Thanks John and crew.!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"E TUCKER","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWB3pVnVQUwM1AUu3YOVViDq_42KgsmOWQwLPLiKTrEyamzI_5W=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"John and his crew installed James Hardie siding for us.  We could not be happier with their work.  The entire process was efficient and fast, saved us some money over competition, but did a quality install.  Clean up and removal of old siding was excellent.  The house looks great!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Am7v9Z4O7e2slnRHHiIiPT5321dnIVmsQwWv1qqDTLyDNctsQGX6a9fUgaA8-9Y2BeJkL-Q3d5uwtp2OEKSlr8HcpcPVDQ9ucGjTguGLJYLqFvNY-WrCU0SV2huvYYSG77bEi=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2PuC_HQU2rBKmRYqm9M__FqMNaq1RcC4CbhG_n7lBYftvlyMjBCl13kjcxhDv2Ey8W-syWJw0uVQ5MBySU-NMdbrACaQP9wM2leE_Pk0H5UNKqqlxsbhyXcTTDu2BNTynb2HbN=k-no"],"When":"2025-1-23"},{"Name":"Justin Shea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBhjdx9Q4hn_tue7pQvLCqM7fMnoIfRBlkT1mvDQ2Mo9L04g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I seriously could not be happier with the quality of the work and the respectful sincere nature of the crew. The job was delayed because the delivery driver was afraid of my driveway but John worked with them to get a solution and saved the day. I would highly recommend Green City if you want honest quality work. My house had already been partially resided before I bought it and the difference is night and day. They even fixed some of the previous flashing for me from the previous contractor that clearly either didn’t know what they were doing or didn’t care and refused to let me pay them extra for it. I cannot stress enough that if you care about quality and professionalism do not hire another contractor or you very well could be sorry and not even know it until years later when you siding fails potentially rotting your house underneath and your warranty voided for incorrect installation. If and when I need more work done I will not be shopping around. I have a new contractor in my contacts and I’m deleting the rest! I respectfully suggest you do the same.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katherine Steen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtj6w9Ck-a6vMnLAcYQBmnk62_ZhE4raPfr45f62RKsgJcjawxyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"John was professional and timely. He was able to schedule a quote visit remotely, which was key since I live out of state and we were doing improvements on our rental home. He took the time to educate me about the process, education, and materials that he would use to complete my project. He explained the warranty and work timeframes. He wasn't the cheapest but he really proved himself when he had to work with the roofers to get the project completed with 12 hours to spare before my renters moved in. All-around excellent service. He sent me pictures and videos of the project and was responsive via phone, email, and text for the duration of the project. Hands down the best service I've ever had from a contractor.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0hZT0wjH-FQ_cIGsVdjQoPxQ3mLXbMq6z0Po_hnwQ1OXfYSctDh6JAenpXCl1horh5DcsmO_RJR43PLwkdO1P8sxxZeCMLa4TlzSJcFKbqkOrb5eLuI7IgUgd8v_6A2AYeOIhDIA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn350DysDLHscqJ_xJ3yGeVAYiSEOYO2BIlpK_zzxoT2oU64BdAnRuKuDtWs2uCIB7KvjIK5ts9Xj9pHKwSGS4VnS07NncUDOzMO4Z07AN3YyIOqW9P5ckb1XDb4yO-VbNcVSL8=k-no"],"When":"2023-2-7"},{"Name":"Scott Bothel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-cqkOvqPUoHdl1uZvDh4tbamMiHRtLGmWV9JV0wDtXMBK_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"John and team helped us find the right windows for our commercial building based on budget and design needs. Custom order was managed ad expertly installed by his team. Communication was great and final product is excellent!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theresa Crock","ProfilePicture":"ht