work ans craftsmanship.\n\nA major strength we observed was Jose’s ability to collaborate and manage the job site. Since we hired a designer for this project, effective communication was essential, and Jose was great at working with them to prioritize creative decisions. Furthermore, we occasionally had other specialized contractors on site (for masonry repair, countertop installation, and railing installation), and Jose always managed the logistics smoothly, giving them the necessary space and access to complete their specialized work without interference.\n\nWe highly recommend Jose and Cruz Construction for anyone undertaking a large or complicated renovation.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2wLxFWPT1ejTL1AvxaHSENtIubANKIdaDJ-HI5lWFj1PK_t4ERqSLvmGnZE9Gfw7PqGKFbUG2ncrjDV6_jshGZqAV7CacG74l7xPEo-XkkjlzGNZYb1ar-lJCIoJRgny2zb2xU6xAgouM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn31fa3ont9LZpRZMILn4VRnSQ6wJPx6XBrT5wq-JvR-AnMXRbX_v9OBu44dDJ2ndicJlt-99xEyGs3rEND7fjgkFyKZVKOZT_4ve5kVuzrkqTnOKvxnEFthKvw-Iv_OU87v7L7LeC-0tkLy=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0dW9gAxEMmLanVPXGOK-f2XHUVsWRM1kv7nmLBZU6rlwz3EgogiGMyhPzfRety64x1Bnw84U2F_Uodq-Wd0oz6QWdxb5zADWGZ-Yzb0NE5W0wBS9wgy-E0Hj4sFzYFG-hOuZIre4TRuLQt=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ll25zfKlnvyayyB2g-euabFs_uHVnZxkItlRHo66yy60sGVqNqnTGzs_AXOadX8fJK20ib4g1w0CpG2Q16PuWIEaoSkxuNm4lI0moTBy76sD2Tys0Okm7A1aq3m0ETn6Ga6shoP3n0lw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1OwZHA4oGEX5fRHKQKSmjDJ9vj_0Cf2tJAhaNVbH2EnhtD4OBGUPMTz7BW61dxbPzaeBm6v107F1nDEa0gPGeWwRYJefUVv9t008f9bWg6OegqknVUbR1o57BV1g8uc7-FgLDnms354Os=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-26"},{"Name":"Felix Youjong Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtkmHMW4CKDFJkPe8zmggdYvVMyc4lHdqJF3tp3qQwEyRMkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jose and his team were amazing! I talked with at least five different companies but Cruz Construction was the best. If you see this review, you do not need to talk with another companies. His price was fair. His quality is good, and also his communication was great as well. Strongly recommend Cruz Construction.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Vasquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAhyMXD3IFnTaXlCHFXF9RUzvcF7ObxzG_u2XXR-goXHBvuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cruz construction and Renovation LLC has been a breath of fresh air to work with. We contacted a number of contractors to do a complete remodel of our kitchen before ultimately deciding to go with Jose and his crew. This was one of the best decisions we have ever made! From the very first interaction with Jose, he has gone above and beyond, well exceeding our expectations throughout the entire process.\n\nJose stayed true to form ensuring he would not sub contract this job to others. Unlike previous experiences with other contractors, Jose personally worked on our kitchen from day one. He kept his crew small and efficient. Our biggest concern with any contractor was communication. Jose consistently provided us with updates through the kitchen remodel. Nothing was done without first communicating with us. As far as the design on the kitchen, Jose was encouraging and mirrored our enthusiasm. He gave us great suggestions when we weren’t sure about design aspects. He never pushed his own agenda, but rather wanted to make our vision of our kitchen come to life. He provided sound suggestions along the way.\n\nLastly, Jose and his crew exemplified professionalism and excellent craftsmanship. They were punctual, on time, and always cleaned up at the end of the day. Their attention to detail is what really set them apart. During installation of our backsplash, if a tile was slightly off, Jose would not stop until it’s precisely aligned or he would simply redo a section of the kitchen until it was perfect.\n\nIf you are on the fence or unsure about which contractor to hire for your home improvement, I urge to contact Jose and Cruz Construction. We will be hiring Jose again for our guest bathroom in the near future. You will thank me later.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn06dYcVCGVxoGVmd6KHZOEh2CZuqQTrJzsUXqnQRd5_hXLZBFdbU3crsZgCD4iW8NAoocZr81Vr9QzXX65qm6vYv3n2FkM6Syr8E8HiOw7LNSELgXbg0uOOLh9PWu9td0R36as=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn33ONJPAA8o0Y0DoemM-EE2pkJ4heuSZhvVructlNnpSaVFcT8PZP-TWF9X-uNuB6VfmKMMBniWyLhhM44fTV6JtUdpPRjrRpu4QhMn1uxJkqO_iwzddJNokwXkF93HuR06TDlgVw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1U9d_oVqIDEBpaDkoDk5JR6LySTaiAjKfVPKhV4T0p4a7N6Dr17TaVWg1AhWT1YiQRosa1zoUP_Sz5hbYp5mpFUjblSSpavHo7v6sYSnAAEXmj0tzajb5VwtrvH0pBHydh2nAR=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3MepeY3owJ8BJUDwOOY6p6sye_WdzRVgNDe8mfZVc9BBUtATU2O3OCGALir8Hchdbf6rXIKd-BekXHmWozW5vMC6956AS4D00k6ub9JJYnuu06n1Di2jflbVxs5h2OmBGbnYSqug=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0uKcF2zQ0WPFGkM-H1Um7Ycu85UotlXMCzRtD979aDjm6BapSQSMR7bZ9G_Ud-AbSSpN48BNKDiLrSc3a9Tepg-RtAV7dsjQg9Ec5vo9KatFcQngTe9aP1M-mtfm0xquTizpam=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn34WvNdgg3kV-8giGgiUMReh01LRoQuYLBNKAx6GNUYXB0ljth0d0WZZ_8JAj7mu-udxT18DbqUmCy-RniN9NM3AsLhoAe6wAzbIqRvlVnDMFajPF9Jd3vWihlaT2BqFuaXaVT3Eg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2G0t5IINnlTlI9749YlQlO72CnRVbO_1lNzCqzJzQH4OQo9xT119KSlhUzTwrcK8ghZ3WtwAbiasDUwj1m-Zowb_3Ah8uyC3p4ukwQdFua4CfSKqrNHoZf6T8MTNxdCvrMZ4XP=k-no"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Phil P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQvS6AsiDnLdW7ZgnktpB8VHBqGLeYQv-g1ElznewS7cG29OdY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jose and team did a phenomenal job on 2 large projects for us: a complete shower tear down / renovation and repairing of our hardwood floors in a room which had buckled ~2 feet high and split due to water damage. Jose worked with us to customize the shower layout. He was also able to salvage much of the damaged floor and re-use it which we greatly appreciated as a close match would likely not be possible. Billing was itemized and clear and aligned very well with initial quotes. His crew were extremely professional with high attention to detail and cleaned up spotlessly when their work was done. I have recommended Cruz Construction to my friends in the area and I will definitely be using them again for any future projects.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ggtbLbGmw3tHlAphXtTY4iJJX9UZCaYaURBg_99_RGViPgSkjzUT4A57cG-La_M5M4Y1B4gySBbNxfAaqyOofCkv95HjNEK9xWENGckh3v_JR_XljqbhkNpOigc7Ptmb2OIs25g=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2rKs_Z-eYLs2ia6CKVS5gc8yzbB6Z_VoQcskrt4yhjgPh4ffnN0gpX7zH_ma1BNaOrIwE2irHs1Ru_6J8eagdF6Ddt72947DSQqbz51-5LM9LumAdFYkZqhXCsxiy6hhPZJTOX=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2IDX3jmggVPg4-vUuTXPx_a4Oi3XE81iEUmdAhZ0V5yAglzsfPQkUXzNf9BlS2n-I2faloURXulzDki2Az4IdMPcR0YsDW1gEK077wwMLx9LXPuio9-2pte-smC-58l2fEfajMtg=k-no"],"When":"2023-12-5"},{"Name":"Andy Spieth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmi6qVds6hZncY4shUDMk-KxUmcai7CagtQeweiBNZqDY5y8SH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Jose \u0026 team after deciding to stay in our home a bit longer.  In order to do so we wanted to expand our home to the outdoors with a significant deck. We interviewed about 6 different contractors and decided to go with Jose, and WOW, he did NOT disappoint. He worked with us every step of the way trying to figure out the best options to stay within our budget. He customized (and built) everything from the railings, stairs, privacy wall and the roof. We will use him going forward for every project that we have, no doubt. If you are looking for someone creative and reliable, Jose and team are the right team for you!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3XBJtNm_Ze65v5BPLCZlXm8yiOXzyKCahTYITOjFO0Z0MdehuGDyvkaV4uJpGdcYlg7QGD_w-6Gc