SBNxncWN7GIpdAtqIjwr3eI2uz3AvjgE7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"John and his staff created a living space for our family that is so beautiful.  They remodeled the entire condo, moved walls, added a master bath, and moved the laundry room.  They worked with our architect, structural engineers, and inspectors to complete the job.  I have used his staff for additional work I have had done and will use again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kathy karner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3fUttjmvYp4QJwgegQJ0lPXJCQNXPGlwoBmlMjGulSA6SJ0kE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Third Arm did a fantastic job on my townhome remodel for sale. They were able to schedule the tight timeframe I needed, rolled very easily and professionally with changes in scope I asked for before beginning, communicated well throughout, offered really great options during (ie, I’d contracted refinishing the kitchen cabinets~ he found a great deal on all-new cabinets for just a small amount more, *really* enhancing the resale value) and both VERY important to me: finished when they said they would so I could hit the market in optimal timeline, and stayed in budget. The scope: All new kitchen, new paint and flooring throughout the 5 level townhome including cathedral ceilings and ALL those stairs, add a closet to a bonus room, new glass front for gas fireplace, start-to-finish 3 weeks including initial tear-out and demo. (Pictures shown in-progress)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2yw_6ZlwFHd-n8kimKI_JKQ35VYlWUo_oNg34ixFMYJsMjN0ROucEfvWENLfqrWEWQ3MO3eVrGd1XDM68UV2BFvd_el2vJGl3Ook1hmV_olSQVG_9m9NUlDN2LcJPGJy2-qYZxEA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn14HPnzUc3RbzGO7I502U5Mal35GhfqNa1Shx_nIOAnoDZHWYbMTV6Qp8cqrr4NeM3r52unFy1K9Y0PF5ycizxrplPAn-iIJbjWVYvdg2W1jXUqK9gsDgAW0JyPlEP_XSKgp2P-=k-no"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"Korosh Mohsenzadeh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGFVfFs9Qt-Wj7y50Ysd3qjKYDfU-wN6t8fF2t0ITZKi4_cw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"John and his crew at Third Arm Construction replaced my flooring, carpet, and did some electrical and handyman work.  They did a great job, and were quick about it.  John was always responsive when I would contact him, and kept me updated with the progress.  I would highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Veals","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIc8mXDWfR-4a1SUmmqWwVuIdcQ-j6IvboU8lYPwMYXmMMmoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Third Arm Construction completed a variety of projects inside and outside my home over 4 days’ time, as promised. Outdoor work included building (including replacement of a small balcony), pressure-washing and staining, removing vegetation and discarded items, and replacing 2 exterior doors. Indoor work included repairing and repainting textured walls in several places and smoothing/staining a ceiling beam. The crew arrived on time and was well-prepared, thoughtful, and thorough. I am very pleased and would definitely hire them again.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
