 it possible for our family to remain in the home for the duration of the project by keeping a tidy work environment and respecting our schedule. We also appreciated their promptness when challenges arose during the project, they always came to us with multiple solutions. HCC truly stand behind their work too - if something pops up, even months later, they will make it right. Very pleased with the results and will be using them again for future projects!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1pxzGCPauqwp3KwwV0ryN-3PCC-X-NliW4wCmcZ_LyB-cf_Vme6oU1FwaFdNA1Opv3ZKKhLvN5COdKXbhIoftANyOAkOcyrWVQ5_z5nH6qpi40W4nKFkF-3ac4-6LY840BJ_RXlU6zJSpe=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3V63yhAxvR7hbVU7KJJzI14cJ-mRcr9334nS_fIvW9j6hadkFkdufOyo_Zrmn5cm1PfFNT3N1C7AWkf0yCdLUzn-5wCsL4sax6jqcO4qqRTbblnI8i5a0niOxU1eXE-aiiDJps6X2GWgI=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0udZEvSYsJkNxxWsxZhKryw4CyWW3HKnYwa_x1p3yee-31NgeJ1OHIzp4xlK4yOEq9dp_Z1RGiIv4VTqfGzUGiEF-gmQK0x487oAfu45Vb2LJTusB20EcSrkCEK_3qqhh613DmqouJkEE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1m0CeR7hlqApkILhFXsOxK-tAnILgYHLiezCQ0XZgCwaJzMqclXy5E7kEC5T1KfFGwpt8LZtm-f7fQKxqEU5klb7xKD9sF6HfQV2j6REJNJ4Y9wE8fZKfZWxlsNDNvenuFo-cAsZilrm_z=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-21"},{"Name":"Nick Becker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXL0MsoYPS2hpl_SbwAQ_ErYd8ntF5qTbxbYqrmPVkgOOW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After doing a complete home remodel with HCC I cannot recommend them highly enough. From scoping the project, lead up, execution, and follow through, Sergey worked tirelessly to ensure that everything went smoothly and that we were completely satisfied with the results. They not only managed to complete the entire project with an aggressive timeline, but every single detail of the work was beautifully done. Any surprises that came along the way were handled and resolved without any additional stress for us.\n\nOutside of the work itself, the management of the project was fantastic. Regular updates any time of day, pictures of the daily work uploaded to a portal, and a timeline that we could see to visualize when everything would be done.\n\nAll of this to say that I was blown away by the quality and ability of HCC to take such a large scale project and deliver on every front. If I ever had a need for another home project in the future they would be my first call.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1tGm_cUyyrcUvEmBm-RT58bbFcBudVo2rWrzUrv3WKwVmStHL-JZR_qGcefGyzAJpLCIJEt_VGTK-5cXICG6ZgJFHt_Hf8wK12QJ7RnHJcMzsq7HLIuatU-ZMN13FAmts433E_swD7hk3y=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2CTcBRibMCS-GgudUFvrsIqHR8hx4CsDU2vpYxzfpdSYK0NGratO473ZG24AE5GnyhEZU9VSi_DahoP5_rYkN541bQG3jFguitnKz8ileHaOFah5-7t_IK21ZUTv7G8mgliBsp2gez71t2=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3VVSS889sjArkXdTmLgiDpaEHjBiNAlKkT0ZCEMN_ABlSliTL78WIckc3qjWe2M7czmH0kTuB5FQcWOePTNKx_8pDJBGBYuEPs56Uz_ncq8xL-HeDrLcmi5XZfT95fDrzyOkprifm765WB=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2uGAKxw9h_23GgjeTSXksuwJQn8MZiHnmak1ZZzq5IYSrAXyNVfYQzpS419UwvyQRVTyAbtiTRL2p1SC_1X-Jr85yN5JyzFGM73EurvV3pAMgIAcSXJXkW6nRCxBrlgKo5D9XB97kMRDgB=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1849tOVzKMyIWG4Y_zREAJAkgsL7u39_dcykr5JMSdq0WDmY0OAVQOkAn-5IL7yWvOFv8cxO_Lryl9EQNYQSKbl7b0lHxzROaXYZ3zH9cnzwTpQNoff64k5U3L-0KzGCOSWFij46atCz37=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Dk58WTYuBJJFX7sOv4Kru6dMc58ljhW-jVGD0Eu2iMw4uUzcPUSZ081AKbyF5KrJp3XtS6LALuIHslVSQp67_bpUdDFEsKrwdjg-oEhpgtqiicHbpNNOq-Ar2D0_Zx0K1_G87kJi3KGlU=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-15"},{"Name":"K Conrad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6we7hLS-oDNDmOYpaXSvhC0w5X_t5IcosHnSIAf-3MTmpMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our kitchen and bathrooms remodeled by Home Care Contractors and new doors added all over. The work was great since our house is old and the new rooms look nice! We would recommend Home Care Contractors to folks that want remodeling.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3qRzB0f8e3gfODCDN3QJ3rqiiIWSRBpM0r1oOZPkGx24332s9TfHHhfbHMxtwU3hbMriDQ6taU_OHG1S_jAr4R8qawx8uaU0JVy34FXb7WhVaYwgUOpOhiAT7wEZXyTUv344IMmDPmqV-C=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2CUwCablui0kB1cXEZ08MMIVuYZVeOvfK-N7NNTdZRPdEnc7JJmWiKnsl6meouUnguS_YQaZBof-M91aEeiPTyb_fl3U16fYuMNexw5IElqruOVEq2patS_nJQYwPuwuJJbpuDpvx3lMnP=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-29"},{"Name":"Karlie You","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj-DhUycc0gwr3GQpR6x0TeZmAVcy--W8BAdUL43eQ2sMtJ2Opqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a major remodel done on an uninhabitable, fairly water damaged house. We had one balcony removed and another redone, the entire back deck replaced, the kitchen opened, the garage finished into bedrooms, a french drain dug, HVAC installed, stair railings brought up to code, ceilings redone (popcorn!), all new floors, lighting, and paint, outdoor outlets installed, a hose spigot transferred from inside to outside (because why??), a totally not waterproof bathroom waterproofed... I probably can't even hope to remember all that was done - it was a big job. And it's amazing! They do excellent, solid work. I love this house =)\n\nThere were some security issues with subcontractors, not to be confused with HCC as a company. They often let themselves in completely unannounced well outside of regular work hours, and they let my dogs out so many times that my neighbor called animal control and basically hates me now. My cat was let out and I never saw him again.\n\nAndrey and Alexy were the two main guys, though, and were awesome. Professional, respectful, made good conversation, nice to my kids and dog. I liked them very much, and I know subcontractors are kind of a separate deal from a main contracting company. We put them through a lot, as we had a pipe burst at our old residence and needed the work expedited. I really appreciated that. When the whole debacle screwed up our moving situation, some of the guys actually put our furniture in place, which was a lifesaver and so considerate. Alexy tends to come over very promptly if there's an important issue (such as when water from the upstairs bathtub was leaking heavily into the newly built downstairs bedroom, which turned out to have nothing to do with any work HCC had done). I was always surprised by just how quickly he would come over, when I was just thinking \"Maybe he'll have time on Monday\". Nope, same day. Very reassuring. Paul also did permanent Christmas lights for me on the side (love them). These guys are really awesome.\n\nIf I could do it again, I would be more assertive about the subcontractors, but overall this was an incredible remodel and I've never been happier with a house. Wish I had before and after photos, it would blow your mind (there was a bathroom with CARPET...).\n\nThanks guys!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pam Logsdon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOTzqOfvYz3rQ2lnubWJTRxSCmirddlWiLlyyjwo-dvHAoghJD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our master bathroom is finished and we love it!  Home Care Contractors did a beautiful job. Everything was so professional and seamless. They listened to what we wanted and went above and beyond. They were easy to work with. They were here at our house when they said they would be here. They always kept us informed of what was happening next.  Sergy Nikitenko was our project manager and was great to work with and took good care of us. Our cabinets were built by European Custom Cabinets and are beautiful!  We are so happy we had HCC do our remodel. We will use them again, for sure!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Ar10kGW9LVe1yxiC9zdJMdX0p6aDtr9Kg4KQ-EG74L_-fYRtnYkzvNQg--JIBhSuNzHEE9pr8LZOZQg-Wr9EXifpqZ62JGsjJ5qGrPS44ED2zRarzWxJvjg0iW3SICTYTTdgxAw=k-no","https://lh3.g