ame":"C Lima","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHxPOxGo5rUBZS6-NZL6kmhDKcq-g6pjyN1kPVXeu4izsQtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am really pleased with AXIS Roof. Steve did a very thorough assessment of the roof, pointing out possible trouble spots and options and answered all my questions. Fernando and the crew are the best! They were punctual, worked tirelessly all day and at the end of each day did a superb clean up. I really appreciated them using a magnetic rake. It was discovered that the skylight curb had to be replaced and they rebuilt it so quickly that same day. Fernando and Steve are exceptionally knowledgeable and prepared for any potential issues. Fernando is very attentive to detail and quality. Chloe was very efficient with scheduling and notifications of work order changes. The entire job was completed in 2.5 days. The work AXIS did was efficient and high quality. The entire staff is professional, honest and very helpful. I highly recommend AXIS Roof \u0026 Gutter.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZxNRc_JqN1IRDiCiPzbn4XUbbYF6B3yb4POQ3ihW5VEIT1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with Axis Roof \u0026 Gutter, from initial roof evaluation to completed roof. Estimator, installers, and office staff were wonderful to work with. We had an issue with our solar tube and wanted it checked. Jason gave a very honest assessment of our roof. Another company had said it not only needed replacing, the whole roof did too. Jason, on the other hand, said our roof was ok and we could do a low-cost or self repair on the solar tube. The roof was 17 years old and he said we could go another several years, but it was showing its age. We decided to replace it and get a longer lasting, better looking roof. When the day came, Fernando and his crew arrived. They were super efficient and professional. We had a new roof in just two days and they cleaned up everything really well. Fernando also took care of details I didn’t expect. His crew painted our various vent pipes to match the roof color. He also installed anchor rings so I can tie off when working on the roof or gutters in the future. Fernando was super experienced and answered all my questions. I was really confident in his work. Our roof looks incredible—making the neighborhood jealous 😉!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn14Exk39HaikkJjRAQbcbV4Lvv2PZz-frbOn_YqWbagwztGGecrWvzLQHLSH44oveHrDIuvkyMFQNxbi5xdji4NMvCv6Qx5JdAUw37P7iU265R2PxV0x7Xs5nHXA6MeP7pwYD_kuynum_9p=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn31_UmsMlwS17qVUgDxHcaIpl0isXtROWipHMVAQtDZywLUwImUupvf9sxBmLQRRODnpk_K0FzUAVTWCK_j24Y0so9okcRem2xhMtKqtzNNryVhAugibOiQytI_dkJFm5IxUBpNNVsYiz9E=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3jfHY-2aDiEPPz8Oi9rqh887_fHge7jWjzh1VLYd9KGTGqMH3drGcJuQH-v6tmPWnL2Xd0TEIfmi84B5WOFz5iLhKlPTP3EXXN56-U8Mk80xrCOQhEMcNSZx8gw1ntaRZ94HL7nB7lmG-C=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0d5pv56Jn4vkCHtoQE2GTkHL-U9Zi4acepBwtv5fcnqpLyGWeQh6msAsohkfq0y5rtJwlbd0FgZtI6cHe7ukVsVayoy0AE7CpRGLllc6bfte6723UnpsmnCv_KAVz5TDd2k_uv4YDIeZvO=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-6"},{"Name":"Raymond Emery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYgoaicnQum79p4h4_Iqa9uFBhk18GFlLados7Mg-wkSTmhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a total roof replacement on large house.  I was impressed with the work that Axis did.  Team was fast-efficient and careful with my property. Clean up was excellent. Steve, the sales guy, was knowledgeable and easy to work with, and Chloe, the project coordinator, kept me in tune throughout the process.  I'd recommend Axis without hesitation; these guys are PROS!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2KIsbEObHuZUnIolBt03cX_IBRR5FxQVR1RFGMCy1Q3clJMe5iR_emh9DAR-ws3UGGkdDGkY8VGTWKshIM4ZNWn9ZPdwHbrwxTIJmsW2F3MtyTrOAkyfTFtManBtGPWGO4vMPDcV6X8q3a=