nd ensured everything was scheduled exactly the way I needed. His communication set a great tone for the whole project.\nI also want to recognize Jimmy and Cory for their outstanding work on-site. They approached the project with a positive attitude, worked efficiently, and kept a smile on their faces the entire time. What stood out most was how well they listened and understood my requirements. They made sure the job was done right and exceeded my expectations with their attention to detail and professionalism.\nOverall, Chinook Services delivered excellent service, and the team members truly made the difference. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ST Private","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKo14cbEu2gZjnciwHO2qvpw-8jschM8yXZkvy8yOeWjJAq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Arrived on time. Michael was knowledgeable and transparent about what stains were likely and unlikely to come out. He confirmed the estimate after our walk-through before starting work as we were unsure when discussing our own estimate of room sizes over the phone when booking. Excellent job on our back staircase which was stained from years of dog climbing up.\nWas our first time using Chinook. Good price. Will use for windows and gutters next.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn23TV-wXmGWY4ebzS_h9sH08f2HHb7bv8HGQLRb8nLOU8n-BMWpO9pfVM1ciq3Su9XAZjp9JA41k7opNVqhds2sItI3DyO6kcj7Ohy_hxc10WuhP8TtteTcFRe5uNXR0JH3l-qnCFtjLPM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2eXm0aG6eIVX0jIuRTooqHL4bjIgnlok59XK2daoYZaMqlDLC3n9-9RXqIQ5I78LB4TFY9bwG9WF6kAJBXOx3O8fbKT3oF0CLlIoUxPNQJrtRZWGq2jkAlIXeQePCAtDufaroNjbPOzok=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2lH8m1MlCoLQerhKXJjBUW1rLxFdUyF5RXTnBiuPbQRRL5K3XX4-KKZRkuOHTljQVyWr4z4b_Vw9EvX4aJ21QJ6ajtYwRrCHoZ8Yr948mJ0M03FfrWkZw0svPYgEGyhjOSTyPTv_wl1Zs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Wzda5nsR1U3pxhWZHxPx7JWfI4dWnzbj_NDzLuDTOnpIrfXy8nNb