 the next five years as a result of the roof treatment. I couldn’t be happier with the outcome, my roof and gutters look fantastic, and the guys did a great clean up around the house. I’m so impressed I’ll be looking into their other home services too, because even though I like to do things myself, I’m getting too old to be climbing around on my roof anymore. Chinook Services has truly earned my respect and recommendation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Keoni Alena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwJLEPHp_-fiWgrJO7vCTuKlVoQlqA2KXIEHVksHeO-URPdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been using Chinook services for more than a decade. They are so courteous, professional and on-time. Their work shows pride and dedication and prices are so reasonable! Yesterday they de-mossed my composite roof, scrubbed my driveway clean and removed all the storm leaves from December from my gutters. When they left it looked like a brand new house. I am so grateful Chinook is around! Great locally owned company. I highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Prinz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVGc3wlXD8y7WSqDOlsfepwXwHR4oxpF5-kPsMjk62C5HzLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Would absolutely recommend! Did a fantastic job and went above and beyond expectations. I searched multiple options in the Lynnwood area and ultimately decided on Chinook based on value and perceived value quality. While I didn’t go with the most expensive option I’m convinced I went with the best now that all is said and done. Look no further!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michele Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJq2cyR29_UeaOiZXFd5-b84d9fFnndQKSrLPAEReR-CdYFeBZ4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've had Chinook Services out several times and have always been extremely pleased with their results. For ckeaning roof, siding, windows, and driveway. We were super satisfied with the driveway pressure washing and cleaning. Team is prompt , friendly, and thorough and even cleaned up debris from the road and gutter. Thank you again!\nCall for your services!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
