Description":"They put on our metal roof and gutters. Dozens of delays until we told them we wanted our money back. Will not answer calls, gutter came away from the house with the first snowfall of course can’t get ahold of anyone now to repair it. Would give them 0 stars if that was an option","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryan Guerre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_tpCWnki9jFRW9CNzMtzyQf7Xm1J4doB2hDp8P4De8eDKBOl8Bg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They were late to start the project. The finished the project late. They did not prepare the surfaces correctly and they are now dodging my calls and won't respond to hold up their labor warranty. Take your business elsewhere.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
