 situation, and I’m satisfied with my new roof. I’d recommend this roofer for anyone needing repairs, but would suggest clearer communication about insurance and payments to make things even smoother for future customers. Upgrading my rating to four stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paige Maynard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8cibxxBp-7VBfqWmNu7JXYACnIIdAMHYogz8wJuD3lxiEcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an excellent experience with this roofing company in Lynnwood. We didn’t even realize our roof needed attention until Derek from their team stopped by and kindly explained, in simple terms, the problems he saw with our shingles—even though our roof was only a few years old. Derek was very friendly and knowledgeable, which made us feel comfortable right away. The company helped us work with our insurance provider, and the approval process went smoothly. Once the crew started on our roof replacement, they discovered some major issues that hadn’t been included in the original insurance claim. Jared and Derek both came to our home, sat down with us, and calmly spoke with the insurance adjuster to make sure the extra repairs were covered. We didn’t have to worry about a thing—they handled all the communication and paperwork for us. The roofing crew was fantastic, working efficiently to complete a full roof installation. They returned the next morning to put the finishing touches on the roof and left our property spotless, cleaning up everything around the house. If you need any roofing work done in Lynnwood, I highly recommend this company. Their professionalism and honesty truly impressed us, and it’s great to see such trustworthy roofers in our area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Colin L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0tapl-xgOUjlgV2DnGV8Os8swB1sEDnud8xmaR-2wZ3CX-Pc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently had a new roof and gutters installed on our home in Lynnwood, and we’re extremely pleased with the results. The roof looks fantastic—the lines are perfectly straight, and even the aluminum vents for the furnace, dryer, and bathroom were painted to match, so everything blends together nicely. We feel confident that the job was done right. Derek was attentive to every detail from start to finish. He kept every promise and made sure the project ran smoothly. It was clear that he cares about his crew, too—he made sure they had proper facilities and required them to attend safety meetings, which isn’t something you always see in roofing companies. The whole team was friendly, careful, and did excellent work. We were a bit nervous before the work began, but the process was easy and smooth for us. At the end of the project, the crew cleaned up really well, and we only found a few stray nails afterward. We didn’t have to worry about a thing, as everything was handled for us. While the price wasn’t the lowest we found, the quality and service made it worth every penny. We’re very happy with our new roof and the overall experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIMcCwBSE6bLoplS-L6TbLsmCh9-1NJ1llQ3iMRtCNeTx7Wg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My elderly mother in Lynnwood had a serious roof leak, and since I live far away, I contacted several roofing companies in the area. I ended up finding a great roofer through a local recommendation. After I explained our situation, Frederick and his crew assured me they would handle everything and told me not to worry. As soon as the rain let up, Frederick was right at my mother’s house, repairing and resealing the roof. He didn’t ask for any deposit or payment up front, which really put my mind at ease. When the job was finished, Frederick gave me a call to let me know, and I mailed him a check. He also sent me clear before-and-after photos of the roof repair, which I really appreciated since I couldn’t be there in person. Frederick showed true professionalism, honesty, and pride in his roofing work, plus his prices were very reasonable. I was so impressed with the quality and care he provided that my sister later had Frederick replace her roof as well. I highly recommend this roofing team to anyone in the Lynnwood area looking for reliable and trustworthy service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pauline Robinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJflUX26fDKjAqMHGNc8ql9CrP7Erl-uXwpxpmlZI4LZZjexw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Over the years, I have hired Hernandez \u0026 Sons Roofing for several projects, including a full roof replacement, new gutters, and installing a gutter protection system. Each time, they delivered high-quality work from start to finish. Derek explained the whole process patiently and made sure I understood every step. The team treated me with respect, answered my questions, and always gave an honest estimate with no surprises. It’s clear they value good service and stand by their word. I’ve always felt confident trusting them with my home, and they have never let me down. If you’re looking for a roofer you can count on, this is the team to call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deborah Beard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhFKBor6RgfHp6ZsJ-SH_oaqOaJ_n2QQzcA5hA_AU3SpbX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you need roof repair or a full roof replacement, I highly recommend Hernandez \u0026 Sons Roofing. Our roof had some serious damage, and after dealing with other companies who either wouldn’t even come out for an inspection or wanted almost the full payment upfront, we were getting frustrated trying to find someone reliable. From the first meeting, we felt confident about choosing them for the job. Derek was our project manager, and he always made sure to answer our questions, address any concerns, and kept in touch with us from start to finish. We really appreciated the clear communication and the client portal they set up—it gave us access to all the important details, like the estimate, contract, and a list of materials they’d use. They even uploaded photos of our roof before, during, and after the work, so we could see every step of the process. The entire project was completed efficiently and with a lot of professionalism. We couldn’t be happier with the result. If you’re in Lynnwood and looking for a trustworthy roofer, this is the company to call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rodney Dunlap","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAA4DfCqVdURLHH5Iz4wQnMaUg7xjyZwDu-j4LAynzYR8MSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Derek, Roger, Jared, and the whole roofing crew did an outstanding job on our roof here in Lynnwood. The team was professional from the beginning to the end of the project. After they finished the installation, we noticed an issue and they came back out the same day to fix it—no hassle at all. Later on, we thought we had a roof leak, but it turned out to be a problem with a faucet. Even though it wasn’t related to the roof, they took the time to help fix the plumbing issue for us, spending about two hours to make sure everything was working right. They didn’t have to do that, but they went out of their way to help. I was really impressed by their dedication and willingness to go the extra mile for their customers. This kind of care and kindness is rare to find in any company. I highly recommend them to anyone in need of roofing services in Lynnwood.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Martin30 B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5sFAwiswuJTc7jyVG-g9Uof7tMIwqLjiGuyRNwERw_Njr3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The crew did a fantastic job replacing the roof on my mother-in-law’s house in Lynnwood. The new roof looks wonderful and really boosts the house’s curb appeal. Derek, who was on-site every day, made sure to answer all our questions and explained each step of the roofing process, which made us feel comfortable and informed. They used a high-quality, thicker shingle that takes extra care and time to install, and their attention to detail really showed. The team kept the yard and area around the home as clean as possible during the whole project. After everything was finished, Derek even power washed the decks, walkways, and driveway, leaving the place spotless. We highly recommend this roofing company if you need a roof replacement in Lynnwood.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
