eir communication — when they found areas where sheets needed to be replaced, they didn’t just move forward without saying anything. They took the time to show me exactly what was going on and explained the problem areas first.\n\nThey really went above and beyond my expectations, even taking care of realigning my gutters along the way. The quality of the work looks outstanding, and everything was done professionally from start to finish.\n\nOn top of that, their cleanup was excellent. They made sure all the nails were picked up and cleared all debris out of the yard, which doesn’t always happen with contractors.\n\nOverall, they just did a great job. I’d definitely recommend Valiant Roofing to anyone looking for reliable and honest work.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
