puvEbvQjnN-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just had my roof entirely done by NearMe Roofing Company and it was a lovely experience all around. They had come recommended by friends who were very satisfied with the work done on their roof and  NearMe assigned the same Project Manager Dmitri to work with us. Dmitri walked me through the entire process and gave me very reasonable options for our roof. Our situation was an interesting one because we have a shared duplex/townhouse with 3 floors and Dmitri handled the contract and communications for splitting the roof costs with our neighbors. There was very little wait time and the whole job from start to finish was about a day and half with the team handling all of the clean up.\n\nI’m very happy with the work done and will be recommending NearMe Roofing to anyone needing roofing work in Washington","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1qZiCFI-Ds9oPkz2_GdooqLp0d3MvxuLuoEhQjxq623Vic9HxY5UJrBEzp2fXzViai7xUNU-yyd6U3UrH6vYC0FRnDAMchvItmC55SQnhIO2QjD5P1_uxmfEWFwvvf7Z0dLEcON_ItuxiW=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-29"},{"Name":"David Masi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK--QX4MQayZbAiUWFkGMUF1RIEcO9A1V6f8cpaRQLDcbno9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From start to finish NearMe roofing company did an exceptional job. We had some roof leaks in a home we just purchased and decided to replace the roof as a whole. The initial inspection was thorough, all of our questions answered and they worked with our timeline. The crew that performed the work were AWESOME, efficient and knocked it out in 2 days. Not only did they knock it out quickly but went above and beyond during clean-up and ensured nothing was left behind. I highly recommend this company for any roof work!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0-9QyU0_o7VwlPD4lLw0NhcQ54nrsib9Mgj7Ii7dg5UiCCuF0aZVJ3yHrsi8a7AwQlHWXU2vWRNxyLuL5bNlmpPHAVdEtsqGNkF4dKqLI1eWXMSzteYHvLPfBjiUPfrjsZ6zUWYk-B