n, including check crawl space for leakage, to provide accurate quote. Their pricing was fair and competitive for the high quality of work provided. And they patiently answer every questions about materials and process. The installation was flawless with great attention to details. They also fixed some gutter problem during roof installation. They cleanup the job site every evening before leaving.\nIf you need a reliable roofer, look no further than NearMe roofing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stacey Doces","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUURczChBj_3M4jYR8RUdQt41K26Sjr8FSWT6L529tqAOibBPcNuA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The whole team at Near Me Roofing was excellent to work with - knowledgeable, friendly, and easy to communicate with throughout the project. We’re very happy with our new roof, skylight, and gutters. The process was smooth, quick, and well organized from start to finish. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Sekac","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbjHmv6Dt6F7TYMXWBBCL3u93wyJJ4Puj92Sb50ocbHtpXcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our friends recommended NearMe Roofing after vetting six other companies, and we’re so glad we went with our friend’s suggestion! The crew was professional and efficient, finishing the entire job in about a day and a half and leaving everything spotless. Our home is a three-story duplex which added some obstacles but the whole process went well! Really happy with the results and would recommend them to anyone in Washington!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamela Honegger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKSwFHeTG-KT71Rdf5_Ug75aHGzxE8qkACI5GGiTSec0HgTQf7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every aspect of our roof project was professionally done. The roof looks great, all of the crews and staff were very professional, and had an exceptional work ethic. Everyone from the offi