usercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFcA5IXYAjGpp3-vgpE3-7Jqx_m42lo57fqqljctF3LIoVqXC8NQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a fantastic experience with Sherpa.  They were our fifth and final bid and we are beyond pleased with our new roof and gutters.  The amount we were charged was more than fair for the work and time taken.  (About five days)\n\nRobert was our direct point of contact and let us know what was happening throughout the entire process.  He answered every question I had in person (He came and personally checked on the job daily) and was available by text or even by phone.\n\nA few other things about Robert and Sherpa that really stood out were they stood by the promises they made: A very clean worksite and immaculate care of our property.\n\nI would not hesitate to use Robert and Sherpa again years down the road.  They will take care of you.  One last thing.  Don't forget to take care of the guys putting in the long and backbreaking work.  An ice chest and some cold Gatorade will go a long way!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0VK-7dGcTGJKjXsmyUEByYILKbgYxRSuWOE4xGXtGHl4VPrjTi1Bf5VzvfSX8S4DJsKBeTkZCUE-ShQiDbhTzFSRsOaFyE-UmyglhHQTQIuo5g7XJs1GLwZNIBfSrKpGhlWVyQ9Q=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3UTNeqf6eHcN_BpwNCKD2dvp9stTjIf9o1xblIjPycb7GivFk0K7pf8HDkKr7Ex7ms5ZHnZ708cCpWiUpgYW2RZjOAlajFGkBlvwOpjy8evHf2LXQ3ebqrxW6PYbl3U3zxTrNs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2mluT8ATDJ9VbstLub9Q-PKp7zEC5OMWxQpOY9cKFZslrOH8WZUxjhnyG1SuBw6R5UFE8TWEXCvDPPt3Oz5FvUMsDbQxq8iPlMstLzi83bbHk0y0ZAx0N_bWG5zj_fTT-ikKk7-Q=k-no"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"crystal wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6dtQKi3PO-FVtzDm67uJ2__oeKtSW1k9aqrRXtWlulEcGhg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love my new metal roof!\n\nThe guys from Sherpa were fantastic.  I hired them after they were highly recommended by my neighbors.  I really appreciated that they cleaned up every night before leaving.  They were super nice guys and easy to have around.  And even more importantly, did a great job!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lorrie Swift","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzztjCdmCosvj5S34UkVQDp7WZY5VN3xihmZx0uXcKfb2fGg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A few years back, I reached out for six bids on a roofing \u0026 gutter project. We decided to hold off for a while, but I always intended to reconnect with Sherpa Roofing when we were ready. This year, we felt it was time to move forward, so we began gathering new bids. We needed to fully replace our roof, and out of the three estimates we received, Sherpa Roofing stood out again as the best option. Robert took the time to listen to our needs and address our concerns. He provided clear, honest explanations about the various products available, which made our decision much easier. His team worked diligently and made sure to clean up thoroughly at the end of each workday, leaving our yard spotless. I wholeheartedly recommend that anyone in need of roofing services reach out to Robert for a bid. You’ll find him to be straightforward and genuine.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Elperin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-7N7y4CpGbQCsw-mR1bodKclQZ5HeL_jN6t1k7pTUBI0plIU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sherpa roofing did an amazing job on my home. Came in ready  and worked hard until the job was done. After leaving each day they cleaned up after themselves. Great work Robert and team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brent Gambriell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUqnvuhgpXkOfm8c8KKygTIrMILDSewsnzLod-wagHVi9T5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mike and his crew were a pleasure and easy to work with. He always answered the phone and texts with any questions I had. Very professional, clean, hard working guys. Did an immaculate job on my roof the way I wanted it done. They figured it would be done in 6 days but it only took 5. I highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"L Pasc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4vV6dV_I7XAmIkEaDhrwIqUAb1WNRJxTdeBHcz8FUf775dg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sherpa Roofing was one of two roofing companies that a highly regarded construction company recommended to me for a very large and complicated roof replacement. Robert, the owner of Sherpa, was very responsive, and clearly and honestly described what work needed to be done and what it would cost. Because of his clear competency and professionalism in the bid process, I chose his company to do the work. His construction/roofing crew was very capable and professional as well. My roof looks fantastic and every little corner and crevice was attended to in the re-roof. I highly recommend Sherpa Roofing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"julie razwick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOg2QFHqs7YzU_hMe9mc5Sln5R_BNi6lF231qkJE-7Vpcqjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Richard and John were on time, very professional got right to work and even did a few extra things the estimate did not call for.  They worked continually  for 5 hours and then cleaned up wonderfully.  I hardly knew they had been there… except I had beautiful new gutters!\nThank you!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
