lculation materials but then like a boss made things right.  His customer service skills are pretty good and his boys did a great job and the price was excellent.  I would recommend Elite Contractors Group for your roof 100% absolutely!!  Mine was done in 2022 and I have no regrets they did a great job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"joy zhuang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIbzucgylbENSgVFC337FtS7vaYXrbClbbWDlbeKcN4zeKeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Elite Contractor/ Patrick Boyer when I contacted a roofing company with the request to fix a couple of small dormers on top of the roof. Patrick convinced me getting a new roof (mine was 20.5 year-old roof) together with dormer repairing is the good choice in the long run. It was a happy experience working with Patrick and his crew, as they moved fast in the whole process, from quote, plan finalized, shingle color selection to installation, and ensured quality work done! Once a small trim work not up to Patrick’s high standard, he rolled up sleeves and got the job done. I appreciate Patrick’s hands-on as the lead and easy to work with. Their friendliness also impressed my neighbors. I highly recommend Patrick Boyer and his Elite Contractor Group!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"allan miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSwsc7_y8vMS0S0Lxr7mI5598Vc_8Givq_mGTQ-h-RykC5oA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Patrick came out and found the problem right away. They came out and fixed my leaky roof. The prices charged were very reasonable. Great company to have your work done and friendly to. Did a good job of clean up. Would recommend them for all your roof needs.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1TOpEM3eL5M1aEhJwuPLa8HNDy52daDVJSDSIxmbIJ4fb3xYd3WYpgd9Jj9pNrYlsU_eZXXB-b6tHg95qnIOHYNWZ3zTs7iXflvqtAk7et-o2i6EZHmA4sUrg8nW51Sph35RF4=k-no"],"When":"2022-10-5"},{"Name":"Bob Comstock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuEBEMpDVRZ5hVvWbQwlKFOcJeCa76yzLMfAUnd1WYq8ZtTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had quite a wind storm Friday night that ripped off a pile of roof shingles from our home. The next morning, upon seeing all that roof damage (including missing tar paper) we started calling roof repair contractors, then began to panic when no one was available for immediate repair. We had a hole in our roof and it looked like water damage was inevitable. We then had the pleasure of finding Patrick at Elite Contractors Group LLC who understood our dilemma and sent someone to do a temporary emergency repair.  Thanks to him, the downpour that came the next day didn't leak into our house.  Looking forward to the final roof repair which is promised in a couple weeks. Thank you Patrick and the crew of Elite Contractors Group.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bonita Easterling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlNkyoptIPpXQ5bgCyRcs2DVCZ29gHHRKToFHJZnDaFHW3yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I give Elite Contractors Group a 10 for the professional workmanship and appreciate Patrick Boyer coming over to my house on short notice to repair my new roof with a temporary patch due to a large branch landing on my roof during a high windstorm.\nI will definitely refer his company to my friends.\nThank you for your high dedication to taking care of your clients.👏","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Colvin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXs0bBYHj7bScKrTxLWDuensfygOnnoHB1_NKJaMRM-psuM14_M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Patrick was great to deal with and very fair in pricing.  His crew was nice , professional and finished the job quickly.  Would definitely recommend. A+","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandi King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsR-JOH7dXWPSQWks1gt0f1rRv9Z4BKihDnLROVFvtNVsOICdh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100"