null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wagner Teixeira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXG4wpJg2J04_ZF-o4p4AneUrAQGxISm1ir7NOhJvcZgQiz3kOdpw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent gutter cleaning service! The crew was on time, very polite, and extremely careful around the house. They explained the steps, checked for any blockages, and made sure the water flow was perfect before finishing. They even provided photos to show everything was clean. Great service and great people. Five stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wagner Geraldo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQ97zRrXjHlIx0tnrDhw2VHtrBwBRM4-vn_rgz6rNtOdXwTqpYtA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so impressed with the soft washing they did on my house! The siding looks incredibly clean and bright again. They use gentle products that don’t damage the paint, and the results speak for themselves. Absolutely recommend Raven Property Services for any exterior cleaning!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rodrigo Teixeira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHcS-rOoUVnWFLqfvmp1Ib9WjabE0ZpS624tCCd7zEAMBb_PbPFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing work! The team paid attention to every detail — baseboards, blinds, cabinets, everything looked spotless and fresh. They are consistent, reliable, and very respectful with the home. I will definitely book them again for my future cleanings.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ARIANNIS MARIN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUN1N1zy187n_g3gnURYvFj2b43dNDnAy46khj-3HYBSiaO1W8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Five stars are not enough! My roof looks brand new. The crew worked carefully, cleaned everything up afterwards, and the customer service was outstanding. I’ll definitely continue working with Raven Property Services for other exterior cleaning needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vinicius Marques","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhf7otSMKCypC-BN3TnCO5Dswj_0bIUu7ju7VrOM9k7NYK61s8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They’re so easy to work with! My roof was so covered with moss and they used the best method for clean all up. Thank you guys such an amazing job.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bud Baker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMM1hpbRAOjgsCKnc5hP4Jst90iSas16Xdafmm-IBB-K9T6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super people to work with. Had them out last year and like them enough to ask them back this year. They do my home, my detached garage and my neighbors home at the same time. Never a disappointment.  Thanks Raven.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
