tDUA\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=231.95763\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"110877178563911756964","name":"Ortega Family Roofing LLC (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110877178563911756964"},"complete_address":{"borough":"North Creek","street":"18002 Bothell Everett Hwy ste b","city":"Bothell","postal_code":"98012","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jada L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2T50OMGvTHwZrlZzfHAyJZ_3QMhPIqQUpvsTUpBlslcajVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this roofing company in Bothell. They are family-owned, well-organized, and a pleasure to work with. Whenever I call the office, everyone is friendly and communicates clearly. They send helpful follow-up emails with all the details you need for your roofing project. Gregory came out to inspect our roof, explained everything thoroughly, and answered all our questions. We've used their services for roof repairs, chimney work, and even had attic fans installed. Each time, their crew was professional, cleaned up all the debris, and made the process easy. We're very satisfied with the quality of their work and service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emma L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLn74XgGqJ1Dm5kg7i9L7nND35dmzMO4jUll0W-53U9RBYzlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We needed a new roof, so we reached out for an inspection and estimate. Douglas came by and we were really impressed with how thorough and knowledgeable he was about what our home needed. We chose Ortega Family Roofing LLC for our new roof, as well as new gutters, fascia, and soffit. Chase and his crew handled everything in a very professional manner and did excellent work from start to finish. Throughout the project, they took the time to answer all of our questions and made sure we understood each step. The materials they used were top quality, and they really went the extra mile to make sure we were happy with the final result. The team arrived right on schedule and made sure to clean up the job site at the end of each day. Mason kept us updated on the progress, which we really appreciated. Even our neighbors commented on how great the roofing job looked. We would definitely recommend them to anyone needing roofing or gutter services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angelica Fletcher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4QfKZ-6zD3ErNKg74ICEM6yOE_RF6T-Ao-iA2AigRrLoaCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a large wood shingle roof that had been on our house for over 20 years and started leaking. We contacted Ortega Family Roofing LLC, and Mason came by to inspect the roof. He quickly found that there was a lot of damage and the wood shingles were falling apart. Mason gave us a fair quote for replacing our old roof with high-quality composite shingles that should last for decades. Before starting the full replacement, he even came out right away to fix the active leaks for free. When the crew started the job, we were really impressed with how organized and tidy everything was. Every day, they cleaned up all the debris from our yard, and at the end, they even used magnets to pick up any stray nails. Having gone through another roof replacement before, we could really see the difference—the team was efficient, careful, and did an outstanding job. We are very happy with our new roof in Bothell!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Baxter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJRgFCUp4o92bnxwLMSrcJKNpLfgxrqo9-eX1wxyLNzKEMXA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed a local roofing company in Bothell to replace my entire roof. After reaching out, I was quickly contacted and set up a meeting where everything about the roof replacement was clearly explained. Within about 10 days, a crew of 6 or 7 roofers came out and finished the job in just a day and a half, even though my roof is big and pretty steep. They made sure to cover all the ground and took special care around my hot tub lid so nothing got damaged, which I really appreciated. The cleanup was excellent, and they even left me some extra shingles just like I asked. Mason, my sales consultant, was fantastic to work with—he checked in during and after the job to make sure I was completely satisfied. Mason also worked directly with my insurance adjuster to sort out any details and costs. I highly recommend this company if you need a roof replacement in Bothell. Great experience all around!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa Gaines","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK49OxC5lbztH9Sh5fd1g6tQqSqyg_IizO7Y-XwIpQWMURX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"ortega family roofing llc recently completed a full roof replacement for two older office buildings in bothell. every part of the job was handled professionally and finished on schedule, plus the price was very fair. everyone i spoke with was a skilled roofing expert who knew exactly how to handle the work and offered great options for shingles, gutters, and other roof-related services. the property owners, who have a lot of experience in construction, were really impressed with how everything turned out. i would gladly recommend them to anyone needing roofing work on a home or a small business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaden Burch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9vPxA60O511aDXiBl1rKk5nj_am3zsUWAuRlOklMmnGAbmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I reached out to a roofing company in Bothell after posting online that I needed help with my roof. Right away, a friend recommended them, so I gave them a call and they got back to me quickly. We set up a time for them to come by and check out the damage from the ground. During the inspection, Mason explained what went wrong with my old roof and answered all my questions. After that, we signed a contract, put down a deposit, and they told me the job would only take a day once they started, but there was a bit of a wait before they could begin. The scheduler called me the next week to let me know they would be starting soon. First, they dropped off the dumpster right where we agreed, then the supplies arrived the next day. Early the following morning, the crew showed up right on time and got straight to work. In about 11 hours, the five-man team removed all the old shingles and bad wood, put in new drip edges, used high-quality roofing materials, reflashed and sealed the chimney, added a roof vent, and installed new sheathing. Then they put on a new roof with a 50-year warranty. The crew worked together smoothly and professionally. They had everything they needed, stayed focused, and there was no wasting time. My fiancé and I are thrilled with how everything turned out. From the first call to when the owner came by later to hand over our warranty and check that we were happy, everything was handled professionally. Right after the job, a huge rainstorm hit, and our new roof held up perfectly—no leaks or issues at all. We highly recommend this roofing company in Bothell to anyone who needs a new roof or repairs. Their skill and attention to detail really show in their work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marilyn Giles","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLotpf4XNn_CBd5lUNt04dXUpf7XCblziYbf6AaCLbaSC58yg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The roofing crew responded quickly and finished my large, complicated roof in just a day and a half. Mason and the rest of the team were very professional and made sure to treat my property with respect. They did a great job with the roof, cleaned up the yard thoroughly after finishing, and even cleared out the gutters and checked for nails or leftover debris. I am glad to recommend them to anyone looking for roofing services. Mason was reliable, straightforward, and easy to work with. I would definitely choose this roofing company again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrea Garrett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBlE2VpccHX-llmIC3TXj6Jp_QP1KNxh8nnZjWZ4zws-Iv9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience with this roofing company. After I called for an estimate, Gregory came out to my home the same day with samples, which helped me choose the right materials for my new roof. The price for installing both composition shingles and a standing seam metal roof was very fair. Mason, the foreman, did a fantastic job making sure everything stayed tidy and the work moved along smoothly. They even took care of some wood rot repairs that popped up during the project. The whole job was finished quickly, and my roof looks even better than I expected. I would gladly hire them again and recommend their roofing services to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
