.  Everyone was great.  They completed the job on time and didn't leave a trace when they were gone.  The windows actually arrived early from the manufacturer and they were willing to come and install earlier but the family schedule didn't work so we did it as originally planned.  Great experience, highly recommend their work!\n\nSee the attached pictures of the windows they cut in but note they don't paint so the trim is off color because it is primed.  I'll do the painting when the weather permits.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3CRGJnfmm6sum9_lAEwrkeUcIRJ2AY--keBJF72plTD_pUghdiKivh1n7xNMlljGb2Xm6YFdyZKJGqrb0qRPjxJM2rBWsrYR1jPyzjBToT3W5JpUWYtB4EGe_36waJnPH4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1SIIsahYNTDdjtW0Z9UkEjaIcfI64uKFBgbmzW8NlFtemMLpzQJYd_6nL8ztL4dgLprh0Tf4oKXlj0toytrr6IYBh5WgMTzmdh_4qCZxqeSdF49050xFne2O4Z9mz9yqG5NOny=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22VAMQbpu1quDV61AgqoCHPpkPR5nj3eOiUx3fnvNlDhPCdpva42inP_v8UcPmeMt3pQEBKZ3oZVL-zhCBee6bb8rebYrSdE_13ssPCxczC7yL3PXdeov-_06Dtuzj1oMe2ZBX=k-no"],"When":"2023-1-13"},{"Name":"Susan Templeton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJti7Y7U4DOxgJfV_Kd6TSaPmSERG607Qw8fg7LDqyiJns-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We’re super happy with the installation of our Milgard Ultra Series C650 picture windows. The windows are beautiful and the fiberglass frames seem very sturdy and substantial. Brandon, Austin, Brian, and Shannon arrived on schedule and did a fantastic job removing the old windows, preparing the casing and framing to accept the new windows, installing the new windows, weather-sealing before installing new trim, installing the new trim pieces, and caulking neatly both inside the house and out. Additionally, the team managed to leave our foundation plantings intact. We’re amazed at how little disruption there was and how they guys cleaned up well at the end.\n\nDuring the planning process, Kerry kept us full