cription":"Dan is very personable and knowledgeable. He helped us deal with an issue involving our roof furnace vent (possibly) leaking into the house, lending his expert advice and charged us nothing more than a smile and good will.\nThank you, Dan!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vanessa Alvarez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDAj6bIZX2iWwmqpzhToKd-XmN2kHmVm7XZNUlubsiK2TMyMWk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptional Experience with Dan Everts at Water Wise Roof Service\n\nWe’ve worked with Dan twice now, both during unexpected roof emergencies, and he has been incredible each time. A few years ago, he replaced a broken vent and fixed a leak quickly and efficiently.\n\nJust last week, a storm blew our skylight off, and Dan was at our home early the next morning to take care of everything. He is professional, thorough, and genuinely cares about his customers.\n\nDan’s pricing is fair, and his work is top quality. He made a stressful situation so much easier for us. We’re so grateful for his help and wouldn’t hesitate to recommend him to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWabk0kpl7fnKKkM8k7JP597391Os1KOz-KpMFzqH6nhMO5bPRU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"second time we’ve hired Dan Everts, and both experiences were during roofing emergencies. a few years ago, he helped us with a broken vent and a roof leak, replacing both quickly and efficiently.\n\nmost recently, during a major storm, our skylight flew off the roof overnight, leaving us in a stressful situation. Dan showed up early the next morning and handled the issue with remarkable care and professionalism.\n\nnot only is Dan well-priced, but he genuinely cares about his customers, ensuring the job is done right and with the utmost respect for your home and concerns. he’s extremely reliable, caring, and professional—a true standout in the industry.\n\nwe highly recommend Dan and Water Wise Roof Service for anyone in need of quality roofing work, especially in emergencies. thank you, Dan, for your outstanding service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean Quinn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUHRJxwW7mUngkOJH_Yz2b0lPWKY-gYBiobhIhfJVWKhat0bhl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan was able to come out and make a repair to our roof which had a water leak, SAME DAY that we called! We are so grateful to him and his expertise. Dan replaced the plastic roof vent on top of the roof over a closet. We highly recommend him! His service area is the Eastside.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew Lim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgEBi3O00TD3CcJSPc7YXC-Iu1nLU6ZyENoJwods1YhVYFfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dan was incredibly helpful in giving us his professional opinion on what we should do with our 20 year roof. Instead of recommending a repair, he referred us to some roofing companies he trusted because we were in need of a replacement. Although we did not end up using Dan’s services due to needing a full new roof, we would definitely call him for any roofing repair/consult needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tirtha Ghosh Dastidar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTOKwKpvaDBc2AFVf685yNhsXcJKAVazlZ7eYvdolRqHFoe0Th=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Recently discovered a hole in my roof from the boom cyclone that went unnoticed under debris. Big roof company was over booked so they referred me to WaterWise. Dan was very responsive and was schedule me the next day. He was on time and able to put a fix in short time. His rate was very fair for the area. I would definitely recommend him for roof repair needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rich Quarre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoVRtHK2LkAyQCeyIsQ4T0Xp8sfOI4iKa2J8zr_depbKVbFA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simply awesome! Dan is old school professional. He quickly identified the problem, came up with a great plan, and then got the work done ahead of schedule. The job was done in a super neat and professional manner. On top of that, I found Dan to be friendly, easy to communicate with, and person of integrity. I strongly recommend Water Wise Roof Service for any roof repairs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sang Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLC9SEL31qh6231FjrMHKoXTKaoHyx9BLZFwR-hQggbTaK0kQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Can't understand why I am the first reviewer. He should have a ton of great reviews. Dan is a great person to work with and very professional.\n\nRight after closing, my inspector found a couple demages on the roof that needed urgent fixes. Contacted Dan and he rushed to help us even though he was tightly booked already, and completed the job before rain starts again. Throughout the process, communication with him was awesome.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
