k-no"],"When":"2025-4-11"},{"Name":"findskye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXhvtudM3fJgMHyBWISZlO-BcXBzgi9iIvpI4Loxte6gNmztbJyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently had our roof replaced by Rugged Roofing and we could not be happier with the quality and experience. Originally, we reached out for a roof leak and John was able to get us through another year after two emergency calls where he went above and beyond our expectations. This year, he and his team replaced the entire thing, quickly and pretty quietly (we could still work from home). The roof looks beautiful! There were some finishing touches that we did not expect, in particular, two areas that were unprotected downspouts when it rained, are now directed into our gutter (no more getting soaked when opening our gate). I was particularly impressed on how clean they kept my gardens and yard (especially important since there is quite a bit of stuff in there). I couldn't even tell they had been here considering the scope of the project. We don't plan on moving but if we did and needed another roof, I'd use these guys again. Definitely recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0r5vJxZeF0l6LYfa823bbfMhbwsPRTnX4DSPBX0D4sErQqa6_y6Yb2IjY9P6dvtVov1L_EXhSENzjxCGNRhIZIhX-5riULtxwmrEBRMm68k8BgJr37ZGpz2gRisUT1svUHzN4AOA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3AZN2qd3TTdJe7zKA1XTtfLTO5xjlbQa-AS05F1Gv8iBCRveGhhIqooUnvtjrogO6YLWFX8dao93YAhIA2tOdf6M7PBhjzUlvULvQLgO5pNXiHzfo-GENz3svDE9k_4sFBkYsS=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Kc_A_RVBxItzlw3AhjuwRJU-boV4_A7mFKD6A18FrC7hNGDRKpGiPzkq-1HdxeL2ptHuNgEGoWVboI0BBkhkpaCblkeGgnnzM0g1RE980mRv9gu5yBHUC_tov0dS_ssosTAo7bQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1FSj6GEbWJmenHUOaWpL4c8j_10_WROF9Twb9E-sjp4dGNmy1ZQMe453DN0hYwxVr7pr6fyGB-wstIHHSeyPDZ_hb7D5Q9FgZ7sBLXW4zMkPlTRIJnj6F0k-P7YefOmS933lCb=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3o