r. I noticed it had started leaking and called Juliano, who came out right away to look at it. He inspected it and found it was leaking around a skylight. While this was the immediate issue, the roof itself was at the end of its useful life. Of the three roofers I had out to look at it, he was the only one who offered me the option of a repair rather than immediate replacement. He was very clear that it would need to be replaced in the next year or two but if now wasn’t a good time he could stop the leak and we could replace it when money wasn’t so tight. However, his bid was so reasonable that I decided to go ahead with the whole replacement right away. He was able to get me on the schedule within a week and now, less than two weeks after his first visit, I have a beautiful new roof! His crew were prompt, knew their stuff and got the job done with the least possible disruption to my household. They were detail oriented and clearly brought a lot of experience. They cleaned up thoroughly every day and left my property much tidier than when they arrived. Juliano was great about communicating with me and kept me updated regularly sending me photos of the progress. Overall, I’m really impressed and will be recommending Soczek Roofing to my clients (I’m a real estate broker) and friends!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2P-VkU8d_34iGuWtLw4-aGfrQSu6yoH5e6syzMUZ15pBxp0XWNP73xb42zqcTezUuH5zCoGXAiw_FK9YSFv1Px06qPmsRokS7BF1U54wSiNigpABx86_XxHogCC7Esqef16Jd6IaBaNaE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1P0NVi9lDHAUgqOSALPhmYouNDXa_C_MNd3JuZ9n_kxTg_qvyrYcy2AA9Tl_3eRDRxkR7wRduZ-e7UyU0xYq6MLSFl1WHXqe-UqC6_k5jJXwdEi1-r3rpD9fGhCq89o4v00WG7j46dSMdm=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn05xrvlixRITYCIuX3HKHYJ5H7xTpLwrwo98PM3Cxgiol62cipQHPufU9sKD72ZUhzhwX2UUdskHMWrwBCiWVFoVi7jq5bkZ51nZXwjfpiERjGu2dsE66V8dlxQ9xV7azDug1tHAfFKhVU=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-18"},{"Name":"Angelica Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUbSiEbU3bcYl3-ctRMuLA5sXfDX5Svmqfu691BJnKyT2CkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Totally recommend!! We had such a great experience working with Zach and Soczek Roofing!!\n\nEverything was so efficient and high quality, from a quick response and fair valuable first estimate, to getting on the calendar to the roof being installed in only two days.\n\nThe entire team was awesome and the roof is great!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1izeCGCHhcVV49wYr72H1J05eieGWNUmz8Znn9uMyaWfzBsGfZ32vaK-hABO9CfhE3lGVgMR1geFv8OIpD1KeHTHFH3UhIjgksfy7gR9Qjj5J7CNMDQ1I-4TS4pnNNWcV5_L-OIvldMeiT=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3UwjAlUh14Wx4Q8VpGLTEXlHLHkwJEXUXv2w3T8H6teVlQmJ6OWhvHkWS8BLr84YTGF0nEyB71GngBLV442aiBXRXcU8udT_sCm-un9AXUEhFLFMgGATfF3tsHghWgVronR82eGq2_Po_M=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-8"},{"Name":"Tracey Cao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRY2pzFp4jD9wpseZKtgwvJd-boVgbeUjA9ALxO0CdeZrCRw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Don't work with them. We hired this company April 2025 for the roof leaking. Juliano came to do the inspection. We had a good talk so decided to work with him. He promised us that they will be using the exact same shingle as before. But they didn't, and they used very different ones (shown as in the picture). In fact, there were other two guys to do the actual repair and replacement job, not himself. It seems like Juliano is just a sales person. Within one year (two days ago), we had a bad active leaking with water dripping at the same spot where they did the repair. We had to put a basket on the floor to hold the dripping water. I reached out to them and report this issue. The manager Vlad didn't respond my text at all. I called Juliano and he kept saying rearranging but didn't give a date. The rainy days will be back on  weekends. Now, I doubt whether they are able to fix the problem because they lied to customer.\n\nUpdate #1: Got the owner response, some of them are not true at all. Here is my reply and attached evidences:\n\n1. \"we completed the repair about a year ago\"\n-The project was done on April 16, 2025. (see text message screenshot). The leaking happened on Feb 1 2026, which is NOT A YEAR AGO. Also, the text proves Juliano promised the new shingle replacement would be the same as before on April 14. But the current roof (picture #1) shows there is a huge difference. You can easily tell these are different products. My question is: how can you assure you can replace with the same shingles next time?\n\n2. \"you mentioned the issue is happening in the same area and also in additional areas, meaning there may be more than one source of water intrusion — not only the original repair location\"\n- The new leaking spot is right besides the previous ones. We didn't have any water dripping situation down through the ceiling before, only water mark/spots. It means current condition is worse than before you did the repair.\n\nIt is very clear that the roof damage is getting worse with more rainy days starting from this Sat. I don't even know if I should trust you any more.\n\nUpdate #2 (February 2026):\n\nFollowing my previous update, the company has since returned and fully resolved the leak. They addressed the issues I raised regarding the shingles and the repair quality. While it took some persistence and a public review to get the ball rolling, the work was completed correctly. The roof is now watertight, and I appreciate them finally making it right.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Start Up","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBdoLrMM9Z_eIARqQ4P7OXSZMboH16PDOJtyZQi3xmc6rR7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience working with Juliano. He was punctual, professional, and very thorough during the roof inspection. He took the time to explain everything clearly, answered all my questions, and provided a detailed, fair quote with no pressure at all. It’s rare to find someone so knowledgeable and easy to work with. I highly recommend Juliano to anyone seeking honest, high-quality roofing services!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"pushkar mishra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvqa0-d6MWue7AzvqDMQHSIbNwS5YBhvkK8KS3Xtt9-Or9Rha5nA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our roof had leaks and the previous vendor scammed us by literally just placing th vents without even nailing some of them down. Then it was an endless estimates from many other vendors who were recommending a total roof replacement for a 13 year old roof… Juliano was a relief where in he provided the realistic solution approach and a much lower repair quote… in much less time… no sales gimmick just pure expertise … we did not use them because of our change of plans but I would not hesitate to call them again for any future roofing work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Photo Reis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFwVImTRCfJnQcJR_o7JgTURpaIyibnaPL4GNt_fKflfKpYv4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Soczek Roofing did a great job re-roofing my house. Juliano was excellent in explaining the process and keeping me informed, and Evelyn at the front desk was very helpful and communicative. The work looks solid, though I don’t have the expertise to judge the technical quality. Overall, I appreciate their professionalism and clear communication! I highly recommend this professional 🙏","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lahyna Isabela","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJrZKdlfwVg0BF-F4g-qVDXceLHKfsb8f5f6Orud7sRkKUUaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very happy with my new roof! The crew was great to work with, professional, on time, and communicative. They noticed some hidden damage during the project but handled it right away and did an excellent job overall","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ellen wendler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDGOEIhnGqUQlDO1N2NxlbQLXFUsWdn7jH6qM_mzpeKNtpJA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had Soczek Roofing clean our shake roof today. Erik handled the job with dedication, professionalism, and hard work. He was courteous and very detail-oriented. We’ll definitely call on Soczek (and Erik) to clean our roof again next year!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
