8ocKNAG1Ij2ASnWSQoDivPRVnDJXuvz2xr9OJGhSFNhXiO40x_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nazar and his team were great.  Super timely when we needed a new roof, they came out assed and replaced the roof all in about a week and a half.  Price was super reasonable and his team did great work even taking the time to answer all my questions.  They added extra vents for airflow without any extra fee and had real attention for detail when applying finishing touches.  Would highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anjali Phukan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0PEIS4rkw0feTYo5X2zmjZ5i0_4LK7SC3hxq7plG1c3-pmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nazar and his crew did an outstanding job on our roof. They were incredibly efficient, polite, and left our yard immaculate at the end of each day. The roof looks fantastic, and their attention to detail really shows. They repaired rotting rafters, installed new fascia, and added venting, all with tidy, high-quality workmanship. I would highly recommend them to anyone looking for a new roof or repairs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Nesteruk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOBXxA-CtFs5XsNkqWbynwrEs9Yk0uHWadcPZMtxfJX8yjRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience with Construction Elite. They were very professional, efficient, and delivered quality work. The entire process was smooth, from the initial consultation to the final cleanup. My new roof looks great. Highly recommend them for anyone in need of roofing services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Андрій Радчук","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSde4B6pP5ZojGXjB-hV0xsXwvYJlLItAbtYdGlaJ8FBXktw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed my roof repaired ASAP. The guys did the job in 2 days. They took care of me. They bought me some shingles and delivered them. Did a demo and took out the trash. The price is very fair and matches their quality. I will only work with this company in the future and recommend this company to you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vlad Soltys","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJgMfmh_UyGHHFw92jClBaiqHw84RSKW_8Fxa37qW-Y6PouA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Roof was done in a timely matter, under two days despite rainy weather. Overnight roof was covered for piece of the mind.\n10 months later no leaks.\nHighly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vitalii Topov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU33bf8qL9_K5NpH4t5vCHx9DUx8b2whd7_qCZface9A5imJl4H=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Did 5 Roofing jobs for me. Great crew, quality and fast. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vlad Afanasenko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwMC4ekwG6fs7QscwAG3GG53AYTn0NkFXaP59_u9f91dEFBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My roof developed a leak. Guys came out, in the heat of summer and replaced my roof in a few days. Did an amazing job.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
