Ibdd7xRL608nLO-EKZlYXqlX8xilMHuQQ=w224-h346-k-no"},{"title":"House","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHBksS-1QhZQkXel-kgXYNMBc7BMVaMv8C-KpTyxXTOq6g2D1NDy7BHjXjBcZdICMkncZVprriRO11EBfVjX-ZWIt46nkHb-KcZ_OWuYf1r9lIl8zqU4mP2WHKTm6gFSM3pDPlZ=w395-h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEpq3u6ILsd-vjXkF1ybJy5HJq50yKsEjq3reCy6vNLoC61xQB1Fzrx5FY2ViR5LT-K3GsWC4BfXaGYXfM_uvFkIc4aF1zkSIpazi6pqaejtOlTjYerg1MPp7FKTTWQ8ymVvdVV=w397-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=6jigDsqZ0tc3rmr1YlyFQw\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=42.7608\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"101222028941960911389","name":"Masters Roofing (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101222028941960911389"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"15712 Mill Creek Blvd #8","city":"Mill Creek","postal_code":"98012","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Leann Rayfuse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXcFRMiy6Sqgz5aKNkx62vGedK_tz3uXQVHgu1-wsxQ1gdMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I contacted Master's Roofing after a friend referred them. The owner, Chuck, was amazing. We had a complex situation with lawyers and HOA restrictions, which he handled with calm professionalism. Chuck spent lots of time explaining the best options for the unusual issues we had. He and his team did a fantastic job and went above and beyond. HIGHLY recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Tanabe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxtOSS8YqowiPHvC-qrIXm4eGUHHn8rCh-xv-5wBPHOivE0yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an excellent experience working with Chuck at Master's Roofing. From the very beginning, Chuck took the time to explain everything clearly and thoroughly, so we always understood what was happening and what our options were.\n\nHe completed the work in record time, and the quality of the craftsmanship was outstanding. What impressed us just as much was his professionalism, especially given that we were in the middle of a lawsuit related to our roof's failure. Chuck handled all interactions with opposing counsel calmly, professionally, and with integrity, which made a stressful situation much easier to navigate.\n\nWe are incredibly grateful for Chuck's expertise, communication, and professionalism, and we would highly recommend him and Master's Roofing to anyone needing roofing work done right.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diane Cressell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSV9-VmrBoA9rInTn5RrhuFHxhmtZyjQP6LFjSMCGuEKftMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chuck represented his company well with good communication and professional services. The project was completed on time with good quality service . I was extremely happy with masters roofing and their services. We are recommending them to our friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Courtney Hough","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKFFXYMS4sAdcoUkQDaHAQ_rqiqFzbD53ss29Fmjzad0oB2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Summer 2020. We recently had Masters replace our front door, re-build 1960s glass entryway, rebuild our chimney, add attic vents, replace rotten siding spots with new cedar boards, and paint the house and back deck... they did a great job! Quality work, Chuck is a great communicator, we always knew what was happening when, and everything was completed in an expedited manner. Would recommend highly!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3eiKItKkjq9x0A0fDZ1IFkbi02fuw-2FuF-Dpa06k7V4_F4N3ts9JjEHHeXRkGLXCBF-DqRJzeJY6y7KMWWtNDYpQH3F3jCbkVRn0NctZ163z6xsbYIssOdmPNIsVZn5fMT0jYHg=k-no"],"When":"2020-9-8"},{"Name":"Hafiz Wardak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0FbUZUR1-IBWuIEsEaWLxWPUHUtVCR3E09XJ-LGTW_ezrDJZobw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are very happy with the replacement of roof of our house by Masters Roofing. Chuck Domenguez  the owner of the roofing company explained the process of roof replacemennt in a  professional manner and completed the job on time.  Thank you Chuck for a great job done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jake and Hannah Rosenberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLKPtb6lAp_cSIoZ11eA1-rMO7eIe8z5P3hMNYw3G4Dw9UiQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I couldn't be more pleased with our new roof and it's all thanks to our fantastic experience with Chuck at Master's Roofing. Choosing a roof was low-stress thanks to their expert guidance. The sturdy, cost-effective solution they recommended gave our family unparalleled peace of mind.\n\nWhat sets Master's apart is their attention to detail and customer attention. They didn't just replace our roof; they went above and beyond, ensuring every essential part – skylights, gutters, and soffits included – was taken care of. The dedication to a comprehensive solution speaks volumes about their commitment to quality. Not only did they replace each part, but they worked around our schedule when we had family visiting in the middle of the installation. They cleaned up the job site at a stopping point, allowed us to have our family time uninterrupted, and promptly resumed after that. It was a joy to work with Chuck and Master's.\n\nTheir professionalism made the entire process smooth. If you're in need of a roofing upgrade, I highly recommend their services. Trust their knowledge, appreciate their meticulous work, and experience the peace of mind me and my family now enjoy.\n\nFive stars without a doubt! Thank you!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Randy Brians","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl5rZkqqw93tJKt9DVbIHjuZAjCNj8n7ZOx5OMzV5NrW_Wu65v=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chuck and his crew were excellent. We had multiple roofs worked on at our large dog boarding and daycare facility - which is challenging because we must always make sure all the dogs' safety comes first. This requires extra patience and communication - and the crew was fantastic at stepping up that way. The bid was competitive and knowing that Chuck and the company are local and steady was very comforting. We would highly recommend Masters Roofing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Delia Ludu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_Sk88zUfPBTVYb0OFTcSDVz3w4LKmu1kcrxE8Zm9brCYZ2_fj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an unexpected roof leak by our front door. While we had to work with an unprofessional, slow and expensive company to fix our walls (through insurance), I decided to research for a roofing company myself. After emailing multiple companies, only Chuck answered back professionally and timely. He was very quick to set up the free inspection and he joined his own team for fixing part of our roof. The cost was very affordable for the repair and they even had a warranty. Great company.\nThe only thing I would point out is to contact them ahead of time during the contractor season (late summer, early fall). That's when housing market and repairs are in demand in WA because of the weather. We were selling our house a month ago and had to do another unexpected repair on siding. We really wanted Chuck and his team again but sadly they were busy and unable to return our calls, so we had to pay premium with some other company for a fast job. Overall, great company though with good service.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
