measurements remotely, which was honestly impressive. We had a great conversation about expectations, and a couple of days later he sent over a clear, detailed, and very reasonable quote. Between their already outstanding reviews and the fairness of their pricing, the decision to work with them was easy.\n\nOnce the project started, we were assigned a dedicated project manager who kept everything running smoothly. He managed the crew directly and sent us regular text updates throughout the process so we always knew exactly where things stood. That level of communication alone put our minds at ease.\n\nThe crew itself was just as professional. They dropped off their trailer, set up for demolition, and got right to work. Every crew member was kind, friendly, and hardworking—they even took the time to say hello back to our kids, which meant a lot to us.\n\nThey completed the full demo, installed new plywood where needed, and finished the entire roof replacement in just two days—and they did all of this during Thanksgiving week. The roof looks spectacular, and we’re incredibly grateful for the quality and dedication they brought to the job.\n\nIf you want a roof replacement process that is simple, clear, laid-back, well-communicated, and stress-free, reach out to Endurant Roof. These guys are absolutely fantastic, and we couldn’t recommend them more highly.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3aVZSrh7mQmX3jdcKyzES1OjDO13bIaehbjtz3p83-t5fMbH8APfjkJqF5c86QmLtRhfSi9ccGqlsT6zyT3jktmCcABZEouIIajVcPg5_xXXP5lnSanrH_qAIqCrbyWJNAncFUBjRa6fc=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn13MTSgrjKlS-3yFbxxMHxe9mfpWldAxezP47-jfoXKTmPpjWDK2_FpFLRpjT-Q13zD8XlqbRsMpR-UgqRBG7YD1W56-koDsK-37u255pJpYKCy8fv3Tkmx0L0wQRaxs9TY8P7LqQPBkWAO=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1vWShmD8scgGE1gHTJVSsPHd5_TKo4tyzySFn-leGzT0ZapESyuLqKbR6hKSHaaXftMwez9sbFtZja18M34RQdiRpL00pe0vFrqKC6xYjrHrGtihJ8VSMFZ6T6jqLo4nxosQYQP8npx5I=k-no","https://lh3.googl