nt.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3h_2DWNNqqD2oW4UebBTJHzMNgT4LP96cxP6yzUE0jHFUsvMD1rNU26ateOmIdZHjvYX4HJkNIuQ1qL62pBONtSdLmpntNChVWOIHg0szzZGCSBebLOyayzkEDbsVgC5eIITwg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2kz2-0Fj42qvlYyg9Bzy8QQokGCjgKzGgdYhl5q2AK55llGOW5Pymgm43NdhGJ8Y0Vw170E8lP-kXmsD15DqT15q_Jf6Zehzu23t7zI6EUlD0LI_J7wrfC3-gUBadltBwVkp4-xw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1iiidHQi8FP72G4n3qVMyPjy9LjRZ4lazoWWoHOAsBmWtsoHMlAQuEaECofk9-cvLXz7o8DgvTV8imvmmKimdJsfuAJ7NaFWD51eKPvuo-Kg25yPmO-1Y97O0HKAyf38OM4QGh=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0yFGqudxiGnN4nxKWuVL82jDOSk0mBnPuxVPWh-o02Hods7Kt00X8DeI15Mt8TY0WTlR5EIuv4UAWj_roy7i-95ZrmgGVupO70vtCgqkjlXkxsBxX4fFGbH7HMY2Vvvn3WQ0td-Q=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1UOwq7TOBar2WE-pOwPx661JVkttwtTXCfGqH4_POz6mvG4tWnjhlIQwAGyvOqCKA228FB0U6z8hA7GRevkOz3jO7MgIFl3npGlLgOydfhWTALBmSIsCTyumeRqaCmZ0rrACPr=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-5"},{"Name":"Dean Churchill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-Hu2HFSl9UCUNApTc7wNWH1xunLB3Ucc6K64hCSjOZ34PbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The technician did a really thorough, careful job of installing a roof anchor, scraping moss off the roof, and cleaning the gutters neatly! He took his time, and had to come back the next morning to finish, which was great (he didn't say \"I have another job to do tomorrow, so will get back to you soon...\" the way other contractors often do...) He cleaned up the moss and debris well. Michael in the office was easy to work with via phone and text, estimate and invoice were correct and easy to pay online.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason Malone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtHbUKx6tEntzTz9ptYeT29n898XelOB27rvxP33dp5iDTvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are very happy with the service and final product from Endurant Roofing. Brandon, the owner was easy to work with and a great communicator. I appreciated his detailed bid and the time he spent responding to all my questions. I also appreciated that his team was able to do carpentry repair work which we needed mid-project when some rotten facia was discovered. He also installed additional soffit vents. Other companies we obtained bids from were unwilling to do this. Brandon and his crew were also very careful not to damage my garden during tear-off and they put-up lots of protective netting to catch any falling debris. They did a clean-up after each day of work. We completely replaced our roof and had new gutters installed. The finished product looks great!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0bfLFAoyiAuT3hDwHNksNVtjh7LbrMoMBPFDUOitz5v_X1qXpbVeQrdEvVtY51NPnLGqN06Uei4ENeAFYnCWBIb-DvCc54_ytBrVSEXWSuD34n6C5TXm9nmXtwZms557essRM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0A-GSZeVvFYiFVdxnMboSYHQjWzribpM1788HOsUaHdpi3YLJQdR7yHoWHRgMGaUXArYPygxgZ_GD6MYCkGPVmBbMRGUIUl6NEsUUX3A8jHJA6jwmbwY4o4n6Ktnw21bkkZl56vw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3yzypXT8fIjfsqR19t7UogczQYcHS2zm66XVmnzowWOfKOnb-E62e3S1KztNG0ut8SQ025WjdNYCcW0gnYF0b6SQ-fEXDHPq252ITDrwR5ml11NjaqzeSQZb36liLH7wTNTZFn=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0kT9PT8IZvbQepBkz_IxEEDrr9tbpW71_As2z3l1_OtunzVj9-34YwzEGuh2QTazS5IwxzrdmJpyyuJggkOPG8tmd_7WonVo0WCw54HRqdfswCFbpS2nolMgKm-u16Tln4QeC0MA=k-no"],"When":"2024-3-24"},{"Name":"Greg Uratsu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv-rXGWFGLGYgp32030RXtYTG96n4sms0N-NJzoxIH3Ev4DwiC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really fantastic experience! Worked with JJ to understand the roofing process, pricing, and details of the job. JJ was very great in communication. Also worked with the owner, Brandon. Brandon was great as well with communication, response time, and detailed responses. Highly recommend Endurant! Pics attached are the Northgate Granite Gray shingle.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/